210
00:14:58.740 --> 00:14:59.940
<font color="#ffff54">What if we ran?</font>

211
00:15:01.920 --> 00:15:03.460
<font color="#ffff54">Took you fast to the ship.</font>

212
00:15:03.840 --> 00:15:05.140
<font color="#ffff54">The brightest crew.</font>

213
00:15:05.700 --> 00:15:07.280
<font color="#ffff54">And headed for the horizon.</font>

214
00:15:09.000 --> 00:15:10.940
<font color="#ffff54">Held hands on deck.</font>

215
00:15:11.260 --> 00:15:13.540
<font color="#ffff54">As we rode west at dusk.</font>

216
00:15:13.540 --> 00:15:15.560
<font color="#ffff54">Chasing the escaping sun.</font>

217
00:15:18.960 --> 00:15:20.920
<font color="#ffff54">There's a world beyond these walls.</font>

218
00:15:22.420 --> 00:15:23.820
<font color="#ffff54">Agamemnon's vengeance.</font>

219
00:15:25.200 --> 00:15:27.560
<font color="#ffff54">Would fall on all of Idlikon.</font>

220
00:15:33.940 --> 00:15:34.820
<font color="#ffff54">Promise me.</font>

221
00:15:36.860 --> 00:15:38.440
<font color="#ffff54">If I don't return.</font>

222
00:15:39.400 --> 00:15:41.420
<font color="#ffff54">By the time Telemachus comes of age.</font>

223
00:15:41.940 --> 00:15:42.980
<font color="#ffff54">Promise me.</font>

224
00:15:44.600 --> 00:15:46.360
<font color="#ffff54">You'll take another husband.</font>

225
00:15:49.220 --> 00:15:50.300
<font color="#ffff54">Enough sacrifices.</font>

226
00:15:50.600 --> 00:15:52.020
<font color="#ffff54">Love's not a sacrifice.</font>

227
00:15:52.420 --> 00:15:53.060
<font color="#ffff54">Of course it is.</font>

228
00:15:54.620 --> 00:15:56.140
<font color="#ffff54">I don't want you to make it.</font>

229
00:15:56.240 --> 00:15:57.160
<font color="#ffff54">It's not up to you.</font>

230
00:16:00.060 --> 00:16:00.880
<font color="#ffff54">Promise me.</font>

231
00:16:02.580 --> 00:16:03.120
<font color="#ffff54">No.</font>

232
00:16:07.500 --> 00:16:09.080
<font color="#ffff54">Promise me you'll come back.</font>

233
00:16:14.660 --> 00:16:15.960
<font color="#ffff54">What if I can't?</font>

234
00:16:21.870 --> 00:16:24.470
<font color="#ffff54">Then your memory won't be making my decisions.</font>

235
00:16:29.680 --> 00:16:30.680
<font color="#ffff54">Take my pen.</font>

236
00:16:31.660 --> 00:16:32.480
<font color="#ffff54">Wear it.</font>

237
00:16:32.700 --> 00:16:33.200
<font color="#ffff54">Always.</font>

238
00:16:33.540 --> 00:16:34.940
<font color="#ffff54">Athena will bring you home.</font>

239
00:16:35.360 --> 00:16:37.000
<font color="#ffff54">I'm not sure it suits me.</font>

240
00:16:39.800 --> 00:16:41.860
<font color="#ffff54">When travelers claim to have seen you.</font>

241
00:16:42.280 --> 00:16:43.860
<font color="#ffff54">I'll ask what you were wearing.</font>

242
00:16:44.100 --> 00:16:45.580
<font color="#ffff54">And I'll know if they were lying.</font>

243
00:16:49.100 --> 00:16:51.160
<font color="#ffff54">If the people from the sea are real.</font>

244
00:16:52.500 --> 00:16:53.300
<font color="#ffff54">Right now.</font>

245
00:16:54.060 --> 00:16:55.980
<font color="#ffff54">Ithaca has no king to raise an army.</font>

246
00:16:56.740 --> 00:16:58.100
<font color="#ffff54">I could take this room.</font>

247
00:17:00.520 --> 00:17:01.020
<font color="#ffff54">Come.</font>

248
00:17:13.860 --> 00:17:14.540
<font color="#ffff54">String it.</font>

249
00:17:24.930 --> 00:17:25.910
<font color="#ffff54">That's not fair.</font>

250
00:17:26.630 --> 00:17:28.470
<font color="#ffff54">You said only he could string this bow.</font>

251
00:17:28.470 --> 00:17:30.290
<font color="#ffff54">He was happy to let others try.</font>

252
00:17:33.090 --> 00:17:34.650
<font color="#ffff54">He'd line up all the axes.</font>

253
00:18:07.180 --> 00:18:08.460
<font color="#ffff54">No one else ever did it.</font>

254
00:18:10.060 --> 00:18:14.940
<font color="#ffff54">Mom. they're bleeding us dry so you'll be forced to choose one of them before I can claim the throne myself.</font>

255
00:18:15.660 --> 00:18:18.740
<font color="#ffff54">The traveler told me Menelaus returned years ago.</font>

256
00:18:18.960 --> 00:18:19.860
<font color="#ffff54">They've all returned.</font>

257
00:18:20.080 --> 00:18:20.920
<font color="#ffff54">All who survived.</font>

258
00:18:22.980 --> 00:18:24.040
<font color="#ffff54">Maybe he is dead.</font>

259
00:18:24.720 --> 00:18:26.780
<font color="#ffff54">And if he is then this is my palace.</font>

260
00:18:28.140 --> 00:18:29.080
<font color="#ffff54">We need to know.</font>

261
00:18:29.360 --> 00:18:31.700
<font color="#ffff54">I have to go to Menelaus to find out the truth.</font>

262
00:18:32.200 --> 00:18:35.660
<font color="#ffff54">Do not because these suitors mean you harm.</font>

263
00:18:35.860 --> 00:18:37.100
<font color="#ffff54">Oh. you think I don't know that?</font>

264
00:18:38.260 --> 00:18:40.880
<font color="#ffff54">Every night they push me to give them the excuse they need.</font>

265
00:18:40.880 --> 00:18:45.800
<font color="#ffff54">And out there on the sea. on the road. they won't need an excuse.</font>

266
00:18:45.800 --> 00:18:46.940
<font color="#ffff54">You just won't come back.</font>

267
00:18:48.940 --> 00:18:50.960
<font color="#ffff54">You don't want me to claim the throne myself.</font>

268
00:18:53.040 --> 00:18:57.100
<font color="#ffff54">You just want to keep me in my place so that you can stay queen of Ithaca.</font>

269
00:18:57.280 --> 00:19:00.000
<font color="#ffff54">I've had enough of being queen of Ithaca without my king.</font>

270
00:19:00.360 --> 00:19:01.320
<font color="#ffff54">Without your king?</font>

271
00:19:02.860 --> 00:19:04.000
<font color="#ffff54">Or a king?</font>

272
00:19:05.400 --> 00:19:08.140
<font color="#ffff54">And you think you're ready to take your father's place?</font>

273
00:19:10.200 --> 00:19:11.160
<font color="#ffff54">Your child.</font>

274
00:19:22.010 --> 00:19:23.810
<font color="#ffff54">Too loud. Melantheus.</font>

275
00:19:24.030 --> 00:19:25.930
<font color="#ffff54">Don't wear your spurs in the palace.</font>

276
00:19:25.930 --> 00:19:28.070
<font color="#ffff54">You're a cowherd. not a horseman.</font>

277
00:19:28.070 --> 00:19:29.290
<font color="#ffff54">And you're a pig farmer.</font>

278
00:19:29.450 --> 00:19:31.210
<font color="#ffff54">And who are you to talk to me like that?</font>

279
00:19:31.650 --> 00:19:35.070
<font color="#ffff54">You're a servant our master left in charge of his herdsmen.</font>

280
00:19:35.810 --> 00:19:38.830
<font color="#ffff54">The master is long gone. you blind old fool.</font>

281
00:19:39.190 --> 00:19:42.470
<font color="#ffff54">And you're about as welcome here as that dog is.</font>

282
00:19:43.430 --> 00:19:43.890
<font color="#ffff54">Hargis!</font>

283
00:19:47.910 --> 00:19:48.450
<font color="#ffff54">Hargis!</font>

284
00:19:50.390 --> 00:19:50.930
<font color="#ffff54">Hargis!</font>

285
00:19:51.590 --> 00:19:52.130
<font color="#ffff54">Hargis!</font>

286
00:19:54.050 --> 00:19:56.250
<font color="#ffff54">Sir. he didn't do anything.</font>

287
00:19:56.330 --> 00:19:57.290
<font color="#ffff54">So that stink is you?</font>

288
00:19:58.610 --> 00:19:59.870
<font color="#ffff54">Leave the old dog alone.</font>

289
00:20:00.430 --> 00:20:01.030
<font color="#ffff54">Which one?</font>

290
00:20:01.230 --> 00:20:02.010
<font color="#ffff54">Both of us.</font>

291
00:20:03.310 --> 00:20:04.510
<font color="#ffff54">What did you say to me. slave?</font>

292
00:20:04.550 --> 00:20:05.450
<font color="#ffff54">He just got carried away.</font>

293
00:20:05.570 --> 00:20:07.210
<font color="#ffff54">Argus is my father's hunting dog.</font>

294
00:20:07.490 --> 00:20:08.250
<font color="#ffff54">His hunting dog?</font>

295
00:20:12.530 --> 00:20:13.490
<font color="#ffff54">Look at that thing.</font>

296
00:20:15.190 --> 00:20:16.550
<font color="#ffff54">Get it out of here. we're trying to eat.</font>

297
00:20:16.570 --> 00:20:18.070
<font color="#ffff54">Don't catch us. he's in pain.</font>

298
00:20:18.830 --> 00:20:19.170
<font color="#ffff54">Okay.</font>

299
00:20:20.210 --> 00:20:21.390
<font color="#ffff54">Then I'll put it out of his misery.</font>

300
00:20:21.710 --> 00:20:22.670
<font color="#ffff54">Leave him alone!</font>

301
00:20:40.310 --> 00:20:41.230
<font color="#ffff54">What did you see?</font>

302
00:20:42.310 --> 00:20:43.310
<font color="#ffff54">You all see?</font>

303
00:20:52.280 --> 00:20:53.820
<font color="#ffff54">Please don't hurt my son.</font>

304
00:20:57.280 --> 00:20:58.080
<font color="#ffff54">Easy. easy.</font>

305
00:20:59.680 --> 00:21:00.800
<font color="#ffff54">Young pup lost his head.</font>

306
00:21:00.980 --> 00:21:01.580
<font color="#ffff54">Show us some mercy.</font>

307
00:21:04.540 --> 00:21:05.560
<font color="#ffff54">Drink some more of his wine.</font>

308
00:21:05.720 --> 00:21:06.380
<font color="#ffff54">I'll take care of it.</font>

309
00:21:07.560 --> 00:21:09.220
<font color="#ffff54">It's my father's hunting dog.</font>

310
00:21:10.580 --> 00:21:12.780
<font color="#ffff54">He's only living to see Odysseus return.</font>

311
00:21:13.060 --> 00:21:13.500
<font color="#ffff54">He's fine.</font>

312
00:21:13.800 --> 00:21:17.200
<font color="#ffff54">I'll put him on the dung heap out front so he can greet his master a little sooner.</font>

313
00:21:27.630 --> 00:21:29.250
<font color="#ffff54">That dog stays out there.</font>

314
00:21:31.190 --> 00:21:33.650
<font color="#ffff54">Next time. think twice before you rough up your life for an animal.</font>

315
00:21:45.800 --> 00:21:46.500
<font color="#ffff54">You're a clit.</font>

316
00:21:49.140 --> 00:21:51.240
<font color="#ffff54">Lies. take them down to the ships. tell no one.</font>

317
00:21:51.780 --> 00:21:53.040
<font color="#ffff54">He's the only people you trust.</font>

318
00:21:53.220 --> 00:21:54.760
<font color="#ffff54">You'll break your mother's heart.</font>

319
00:21:54.820 --> 00:21:56.660
<font color="#ffff54">If I stay. they'll force me to fight.</font>

320
00:21:56.920 --> 00:21:58.100
<font color="#ffff54">No one will back me.</font>

321
00:21:58.280 --> 00:22:00.360
<font color="#ffff54">I have to find out what happened to my father.</font>

322
00:22:00.360 --> 00:22:03.880
<font color="#ffff54">Ithaca will be behind me if they know Odysseus is dead.</font>

323
00:22:04.120 --> 00:22:05.440
<font color="#ffff54">The suitors will never blow that.</font>

324
00:22:05.740 --> 00:22:07.020
<font color="#ffff54">You will never make it back alive.</font>

325
00:22:07.020 --> 00:22:10.160
<font color="#ffff54">Tell him and Tor to meet me at the ships just before dawn.</font>

326
00:22:10.680 --> 00:22:13.440
<font color="#ffff54">What do you want me to tell your mother?</font>

327
00:22:14.160 --> 00:22:15.820
<font color="#ffff54">To hold out for as long as she can.</font>

328
00:22:19.800 --> 00:22:21.500
<font color="#ffff54">Ship's ready. time's right.</font>

329
00:22:22.460 --> 00:22:24.660
<font color="#ffff54">Have I ever told you that you have wise eyes?</font>

330
00:22:25.180 --> 00:22:25.900
<font color="#ffff54">Athena's eyes?</font>

331
00:22:26.540 --> 00:22:27.400
<font color="#ffff54">Once or twice.</font>

332
00:22:27.820 --> 00:22:29.580
<font color="#ffff54">You haven't even asked me where we're going yet.</font>

333
00:22:29.860 --> 00:22:30.700
<font color="#ffff54">Where are we going?</font>

334
00:22:30.700 --> 00:22:32.340
<font color="#ffff54">We'll find my dad.</font>

335
00:22:32.960 --> 00:22:33.780
<font color="#ffff54">He's alive.</font>

336
00:22:33.780 --> 00:22:35.620
<font color="#ffff54">I can feel it in the wind and the waves.</font>

337
00:22:35.780 --> 00:22:36.660
<font color="#ffff54">He's out there somewhere.</font>

338
00:22:37.040 --> 00:22:39.300
<font color="#ffff54">Wandering. injured. lost. I don't know.</font>

339
00:22:40.220 --> 00:22:41.260
<font color="#ffff54">But he's alive.</font>

340
00:23:13.150 --> 00:23:14.050
<font color="#ffff54">More dreams?</font>

341
00:23:15.710 --> 00:23:16.690
<font color="#ffff54">Men drowning.</font>

342
00:23:18.150 --> 00:23:18.710
<font color="#ffff54">Inside.</font>

343
00:23:21.570 --> 00:23:23.210
<font color="#ffff54">Some dark space.</font>

344
00:23:26.270 --> 00:23:27.550
<font color="#ffff54">Firelight on stone.</font>

345
00:23:27.850 --> 00:23:28.410
<font color="#ffff54">I don't know.</font>

346
00:23:31.390 --> 00:23:32.550
<font color="#ffff54">Don't you want to remember?</font>

347
00:23:32.970 --> 00:23:35.430
<font color="#ffff54">Why can't God speak in ways we understand?</font>

348
00:23:37.970 --> 00:23:39.930
<font color="#ffff54">Who doesn't understand thunder?</font>

349
00:23:41.010 --> 00:23:41.810
<font color="#ffff54">The fire.</font>

350
00:23:42.430 --> 00:23:43.910
<font color="#ffff54">A child's smile.</font>

351
00:23:44.150 --> 00:23:44.830
<font color="#ffff54">Good harvest.</font>

352
00:23:45.650 --> 00:23:47.290
<font color="#ffff54">But you hide yourselves from us.</font>

353
00:23:48.950 --> 00:23:49.750
<font color="#ffff54">Look.</font>

354
00:23:50.710 --> 00:23:52.330
<font color="#ffff54">Who's moving that cloud?</font>

355
00:23:53.310 --> 00:23:54.710
<font color="#ffff54">Massing those birds.</font>

356
00:23:56.030 --> 00:23:57.530
<font color="#ffff54">Who's moving the water?</font>

357
00:23:59.730 --> 00:24:00.370
<font color="#ffff54">Who's moving the water?</font>

358
00:24:00.370 --> 00:24:01.050
<font color="#ffff54">Who were you talking to?</font>

359
00:24:04.010 --> 00:24:05.630
<font color="#ffff54">Athena came to me again.</font>

360
00:24:06.250 --> 00:24:07.710
<font color="#ffff54">She's telling me to remember.</font>

361
00:24:09.570 --> 00:24:10.570
<font color="#ffff54">To leave.</font>

362
00:24:11.030 --> 00:24:12.290
<font color="#ffff54">Why would you leave?</font>

363
00:24:12.590 --> 00:24:13.990
<font color="#ffff54">We have everything we need.</font>

364
00:24:14.950 --> 00:24:16.970
<font color="#ffff54">How long have I been here. Calypso?</font>

365
00:24:21.340 --> 00:24:23.200
<font color="#ffff54">I have a home somewhere.</font>

366
00:24:25.020 --> 00:24:27.680
<font color="#ffff54">There's someone out there.</font>

367
00:24:28.500 --> 00:24:29.600
<font color="#ffff54">How do you know?</font>

368
00:24:30.280 --> 00:24:31.280
<font color="#ffff54">I don't know.</font>

369
00:24:33.920 --> 00:24:34.920
<font color="#ffff54">I feel.</font>

370
00:24:51.080 --> 00:24:52.960
<font color="#ffff54">What we have here could last forever.</font>

371
00:24:53.340 --> 00:24:54.560
<font color="#ffff54">Forever is for God.</font>

372
00:24:55.060 --> 00:24:55.960
<font color="#ffff54">We're your God.</font>

373
00:24:58.540 --> 00:24:59.900
<font color="#ffff54">You want to remember.</font>

374
00:25:00.140 --> 00:25:02.280
<font color="#ffff54">But what if remembering destroys your happiness?</font>

375
00:25:03.080 --> 00:25:04.060
<font color="#ffff54">Then I wasn't real.</font>

376
00:25:12.280 --> 00:25:12.880
<font color="#ffff54">No.</font>

377
00:25:13.360 --> 00:25:13.380
<font color="#ffff54">No.</font>

378
00:25:13.380 --> 00:25:14.140
<font color="#ffff54">No more.</font>

379
00:25:14.240 --> 00:25:14.740
<font color="#ffff54">But I love it.</font>

380
00:25:15.540 --> 00:25:16.760
<font color="#ffff54">Stop eating the lotus.</font>

381
00:25:17.500 --> 00:25:19.100
<font color="#ffff54">Tell me what you remember.</font>

382
00:25:21.200 --> 00:25:22.100
<font color="#ffff54">After Troy.</font>

383
00:25:24.200 --> 00:25:24.800
<font color="#ffff54">Troy.</font>

384
00:25:31.210 --> 00:25:32.550
<font color="#ffff54">We won the war.</font>

385
00:25:33.510 --> 00:25:34.170
<font color="#ffff54">And then what?</font>

386
00:26:40.140 --> 00:26:42.160
<font color="#ffff54">Ten years on this fucking beach.</font>

387
00:26:47.340 --> 00:26:48.340
<font color="#ffff54">Let's go home.</font>

388
00:26:50.240 --> 00:26:51.560
<font color="#ffff54">Remember who we leave here.</font>

389
00:26:56.320 --> 00:26:57.800
<font color="#ffff54">Do we have enough provisions?</font>

390
00:26:58.700 --> 00:27:00.260
<font color="#ffff54">We've taken enough from Troy.</font>

391
00:27:01.360 --> 00:27:03.080
<font color="#ffff54">Another stop or two won't kill us.</font>

392
00:27:26.310 --> 00:27:27.690
<font color="#ffff54">We'll raise the sail.</font>

393
00:27:27.890 --> 00:27:29.030
<font color="#ffff54">Follow the southerly winds.</font>

394
00:27:29.210 --> 00:27:29.530
<font color="#ffff54">Yes. sir.</font>

395
00:27:31.470 --> 00:27:33.450
<font color="#ffff54">Agamemnon's rowing west on the known provisions route.</font>

396
00:27:33.650 --> 00:27:34.970
<font color="#ffff54">He's got more mouths to feed.</font>

397
00:27:35.870 --> 00:27:37.230
<font color="#ffff54">We'll find places to land.</font>

398
00:27:37.630 --> 00:27:38.670
<font color="#ffff54">Are you sure it's a risk?</font>

399
00:27:39.050 --> 00:27:40.550
<font color="#ffff54">That's all at Agamemnon long enough.</font>

400
00:27:41.570 --> 00:27:47.230
<font color="#ffff54">With a little luck and the right winds. we'll see some of the world still be home before Agamemnon.</font>

401
00:27:48.050 --> 00:27:48.890
<font color="#ffff54">Come on. boys.</font>

402
00:27:49.330 --> 00:27:50.970
<font color="#ffff54">Come on. boys.</font>

403
00:27:50.970 --> 00:27:51.530
<font color="#ffff54">Come on. boys.</font>

404
00:27:51.530 --> 00:27:51.770
<font color="#ffff54">Come on. boys.</font>

405
00:27:52.750 --> 00:27:54.250
<font color="#ffff54">Come on. boys.</font>

406
00:27:54.250 --> 00:27:55.250
<font color="#ffff54">Come on. boys.</font>

407
00:28:56.950 --> 00:28:57.510
<font color="#ffff54">Come on. boys.</font>

408
00:28:57.510 --> 00:28:58.730
<font color="#ffff54">Just keep the bear on the right.</font>

409
00:29:09.080 --> 00:29:10.340
<font color="#ffff54">Odysseus. land.</font>

410
00:29:14.100 --> 00:29:14.660
<font color="#ffff54">See?</font>

411
00:29:15.780 --> 00:29:16.900
<font color="#ffff54">Lucky bastard.</font>

412
00:29:17.900 --> 00:29:19.220
<font color="#ffff54">We're down to our last supplies.</font>

413
00:29:19.760 --> 00:29:21.060
<font color="#ffff54">Assemble a landing party.</font>

414
00:29:21.380 --> 00:29:22.120
<font color="#ffff54">Food and water.</font>

415
00:29:22.220 --> 00:29:23.160
<font color="#ffff54">Enough for three weeks.</font>

416
00:29:23.760 --> 00:29:24.880
<font color="#ffff54">What if they won't give it?</font>

417
00:29:26.600 --> 00:29:28.440
<font color="#ffff54">How badly do you want to get home?</font>

418
00:29:29.820 --> 00:29:31.100
<font color="#ffff54">Get your weapons ready!</font>

419
00:29:31.480 --> 00:29:32.120
<font color="#ffff54">Agging.</font>

420
00:29:32.240 --> 00:29:32.620
<font color="#ffff54">Moving!</font>

421
00:29:32.920 --> 00:29:33.560
<font color="#ffff54">Borrowing.</font>

422
00:29:34.760 --> 00:29:35.300
<font color="#ffff54">Pondering.</font>

423
00:29:39.290 --> 00:29:42.750
<font color="#ffff54">Ask him why they abandoned their village instead of welcoming us.</font>

424
00:29:44.870 --> 00:29:51.250
<font color="#ffff54">They said they thought we were the sea people.</font>

