00:29:53.910 --> 00:29:54.970
<font color="#ffff54">From Ithaca.</font>

428
00:29:55.550 --> 00:29:57.290
<font color="#ffff54">Maybe you heard of our victory at Troy.</font>

429
00:29:58.290 --> 00:30:00.310
<font color="#ffff54">We're headed west on the southerly winds.</font>

430
00:30:06.650 --> 00:30:10.670
<font color="#ffff54">He says if we go that way. we won't like the things we'll find.</font>

431
00:30:12.550 --> 00:30:18.470
<font color="#ffff54">After years of war. no one could stand between my men and home.</font>

432
00:30:19.690 --> 00:30:20.790
<font color="#ffff54">Not even me.</font>

433
00:30:20.790 --> 00:30:23.610
<font color="#ffff54">Then something happened.</font>

434
00:30:40.080 --> 00:30:41.720
<font color="#ffff54">Chasing the escaping sun.</font>

435
00:30:44.840 --> 00:30:47.900
<font color="#ffff54">There you go.</font>

436
00:31:03.910 --> 00:31:05.650
<font color="#ffff54">No. no. no. no. no.</font>

437
00:31:06.770 --> 00:31:08.550
<font color="#ffff54">Sheep come in flocks.</font>

438
00:31:10.530 --> 00:31:11.310
<font color="#ffff54">Let's follow.</font>

439
00:32:32.080 --> 00:32:33.060
<font color="#ffff54">Someone lives here.</font>

440
00:32:34.560 --> 00:32:35.760
<font color="#ffff54">Yeah. they make cheese.</font>

441
00:32:54.580 --> 00:32:55.360
<font color="#ffff54">Pretty good.</font>

442
00:32:58.960 --> 00:33:00.100
