500
00:43:10.610 --> 00:43:11.290
<font color="#ffff54">No!</font>

501
00:43:12.010 --> 00:43:12.690
<font color="#ffff54">No!</font>

502
00:43:12.690 --> 00:43:12.770
<font color="#ffff54">No!</font>

503
00:43:19.370 --> 00:43:31.140
