504
00:43:31.440 --> 00:43:32.280
<font color="#ffff54">No!</font>

505
00:43:48.490 --> 00:43:49.890
<font color="#ffff54">Go!</font>

506
00:44:01.090 --> 00:44:01.450
<font color="#ffff54">Go!</font>

507
00:44:52.920 --> 00:44:54.600
