00:47:08.890 --> 00:47:09.410
<font color="#ffff54">Sid.</font>

546
00:47:13.310 --> 00:47:14.050
<font color="#ffff54">Not you.</font>

547
00:47:16.050 --> 00:47:16.690
<font color="#ffff54">Are you.</font>

548
00:47:19.150 --> 00:47:20.630
<font color="#ffff54">Enjoy your hospitality.</font>

549
00:47:21.270 --> 00:47:22.270
<font color="#ffff54">As soon as the man's.</font>

