<font color="#ffff54">No!</font>

625
00:58:17.880 --> 00:58:19.800
<font color="#ffff54">He does not want to hear about my brother!</font>

626
00:58:22.900 --> 00:58:24.140
<font color="#ffff54">What's the news of his father?</font>

627
00:58:24.980 --> 00:58:27.740
<font color="#ffff54">I know nothing of Odysseus since Troy.</font>

