631
00:58:34.780 --> 00:58:36.280
<font color="#ffff54">You come here for so much.</font>

632
00:58:36.420 --> 00:58:37.460
<font color="#ffff54">Is that what you're interested in?</font>

633
00:58:37.600 --> 00:58:37.940
<font color="#ffff54">Gossip.</font>

