638
00:58:48.980 --> 00:58:50.200
<font color="#ffff54">Some say he's in prison.</font>

639
00:58:50.380 --> 00:58:51.000
<font color="#ffff54">What say you?</font>

640
00:58:51.200 --> 00:58:51.580
<font color="#ffff54">In prison?</font>

641
00:58:54.800 --> 00:58:56.040
<font color="#ffff54">What kind of prison</font>

642
00:58:56.920 --> 00:58:58.400
<font color="#ffff54">could hold a man like that?</font>

643
00:58:59.900 --> 00:59:01.540
<font color="#ffff54">Tell me what you do remember.</font>

644
00:59:02.000 --> 00:59:03.240
<font color="#ffff54">The rest will come.</font>

645
00:59:04.520 --> 00:59:06.560
<font color="#ffff54">And the men became more and more convinced</font>

646
00:59:06.560 --> 00:59:08.120
<font color="#ffff54">that I defended Poseidon.</font>

647
00:59:53.740 --> 00:59:56.300
<font color="#ffff54">We were hit by storm after storm.</font>

648
00:59:56.460 --> 00:59:57.920
<font color="#ffff54">all pushing us off course</font>

649
00:59:57.920 --> 00:59:59.960
<font color="#ffff54">until we were truly lost.</font>

650
01:00:52.400 --> 01:00:53.120
<font color="#ffff54">Hello.</font>

651
01:00:55.380 --> 01:00:56.740
<font color="#ffff54">We're here in peace.</font>

652
01:00:59.420 --> 01:01:01.060
<font color="#ffff54">We just need some food.</font>

653
01:01:07.030 --> 01:01:08.310
<font color="#ffff54">We need food.</font>

654
01:01:09.930 --> 01:01:11.290
<font color="#ffff54">Can you understand that?</font>

655
01:01:11.410 --> 01:01:12.090
<font color="#ffff54">It's just a child.</font>

656
01:01:14.990 --> 01:01:16.070
<font color="#ffff54">If that's a child.</font>

657
01:01:16.170 --> 01:01:17.010
<font color="#ffff54">what about its parents?</font>

658
01:01:19.790 --> 01:01:20.910
<font color="#ffff54">Hey. shh.</font>

659
01:01:20.950 --> 01:01:21.350
<font color="#ffff54">It's okay.</font>

660
01:01:22.350 --> 01:01:23.050
<font color="#ffff54">No. no. no. no.</font>

661
01:01:23.230 --> 01:01:23.750
<font color="#ffff54">Shhh.</font>

662
01:01:24.190 --> 01:01:24.650
<font color="#ffff54">Shhh.</font>

663
01:01:43.290 --> 01:01:43.810
<font color="#ffff54">Go!</font>

664
01:01:44.490 --> 01:01:45.010
<font color="#ffff54">Go!</font>

665
01:01:45.570 --> 01:01:46.810
<font color="#ffff54">Back to the ship!</font>

666
01:02:01.330 --> 01:02:02.890
<font color="#ffff54">Look out!</font>

667
01:02:23.370 --> 01:02:24.770
<font color="#ffff54">Fire!</font>

668
01:02:56.360 --> 01:02:57.160
<font color="#ffff54">One!</font>

669
01:02:57.440 --> 01:02:57.940
<font color="#ffff54">Ah!</font>

670
01:02:59.120 --> 01:02:59.300
<font color="#ffff54">Ah!</font>

671
01:03:01.260 --> 01:03:01.700
<font color="#ffff54">Ah!</font>

672
01:03:51.080 --> 01:03:52.480
<font color="#ffff54">Wait!</font>

673
01:04:09.110 --> 01:04:10.510
<font color="#ffff54">Wait!</font>

674
01:04:12.410 --> 01:04:13.810
<font color="#ffff54">Wait!</font>

675
01:04:14.330 --> 01:04:14.750
<font color="#ffff54">Wait!</font>

676
01:04:15.050 --> 01:04:15.150
<font color="#ffff54">Wait!</font>

677
01:05:28.600 --> 01:05:31.160
<font color="#ffff54">Turn to port. follow the ghost.</font>

678
01:05:32.060 --> 01:05:33.180
<font color="#ffff54">What if they have ships?</font>

679
01:05:33.420 --> 01:05:35.440
<font color="#ffff54">We need to get as far away as possible.</font>

680
01:05:39.860 --> 01:05:42.120
<font color="#ffff54">We don't have supplies for a blind crossing.</font>

681
01:05:42.940 --> 01:05:44.100
<font color="#ffff54">We've lost our way.</font>

682
01:05:44.900 --> 01:05:47.720
<font color="#ffff54">We need to find food and get our bearings.</font>

683
01:05:50.220 --> 01:05:51.620
<font color="#ffff54">Turn to port.</font>

684
01:06:17.840 --> 01:06:18.840
<font color="#ffff54">There!</font>

685
01:06:19.280 --> 01:06:20.620
<font color="#ffff54">Smoke there!</font>

686
01:06:21.380 --> 01:06:24.100
<font color="#ffff54">Go past. we'll find acreage at the beach.</font>

687
01:06:31.600 --> 01:06:32.540
<font color="#ffff54">Watch out!</font>

688
01:06:36.300 --> 01:06:38.200
<font color="#ffff54">Form a landing party.</font>

689
01:06:40.320 --> 01:06:41.320
<font color="#ffff54">Tomorrow.</font>

690
01:06:43.760 --> 01:06:44.760
<font color="#ffff54">Tomorrow.</font>

691
01:06:55.670 --> 01:06:57.310
<font color="#ffff54">Leave someone with the tenders.</font>

692
01:06:58.430 --> 01:06:59.930
<font color="#ffff54">We think you should stay.</font>

693
01:07:02.370 --> 01:07:02.930
<font color="#ffff54">We?</font>

694
01:07:03.190 --> 01:07:04.090
<font color="#ffff54">All of us.</font>

695
01:07:04.810 --> 01:07:05.710
<font color="#ffff54">Still alive.</font>

696
01:07:16.740 --> 01:07:17.920
<font color="#ffff54">Is this a mutiny?</font>

697
01:07:18.420 --> 01:07:19.420
<font color="#ffff54">That's up to you.</font>

698
01:07:24.090 --> 01:07:25.010
<font color="#ffff54">Give me your bow.</font>

699
01:07:25.210 --> 01:07:26.550
<font color="#ffff54">I'll make sure we eat tonight.</font>

700
01:07:27.270 --> 01:07:28.550
<font color="#ffff54">No matter what you find.</font>

701
01:09:15.630 --> 01:09:16.790
<font color="#ffff54">No. no. it's okay.</font>

702
01:09:17.050 --> 01:09:17.510
<font color="#ffff54">It's okay.</font>

703
01:09:22.780 --> 01:09:23.520
<font color="#ffff54">You're okay.</font>

704
01:09:23.800 --> 01:09:24.620
<font color="#ffff54">It's all right.</font>

705
01:09:24.720 --> 01:09:25.500
<font color="#ffff54">No one's going to hurt you.</font>

706
01:09:25.640 --> 01:09:27.040
<font color="#ffff54">If I do what you want.</font>

707
01:09:27.320 --> 01:09:29.300
<font color="#ffff54">No one is going to hurt you.</font>

708
01:09:32.800 --> 01:09:34.380
<font color="#ffff54">My name's Eurylochus.</font>

709
01:09:34.460 --> 01:09:34.920
<font color="#ffff54">What's your name?</font>

710
01:09:35.360 --> 01:09:36.020
<font color="#ffff54">Cersei.</font>

711
01:09:36.380 --> 01:09:37.020
<font color="#ffff54">Cersei?</font>

712
01:09:37.260 --> 01:09:38.500
<font color="#ffff54">We need food.</font>

713
01:09:38.720 --> 01:09:39.160
<font color="#ffff54">Badly.</font>

714
01:09:40.080 --> 01:09:41.300
<font color="#ffff54">I have food.</font>

715
01:09:43.020 --> 01:09:44.520
<font color="#ffff54">Lots of food.</font>

716
01:10:05.580 --> 01:10:06.900
<font color="#ffff54">You let me?</font>

717
01:10:10.000 --> 01:10:11.120
<font color="#ffff54">Your weapons.</font>

718
01:10:11.500 --> 01:10:11.860
<font color="#ffff54">We're armor.</font>

719
01:10:13.360 --> 01:10:14.660
<font color="#ffff54">Put it out the back.</font>

720
01:10:57.580 --> 01:10:59.140
<font color="#ffff54">Do you like my meat?</font>

721
01:11:00.420 --> 01:11:02.420
<font color="#ffff54">Why do you have so much?</font>

722
01:11:03.340 --> 01:11:05.780
<font color="#ffff54">You never know when strangers will come.</font>

723
01:11:16.460 --> 01:11:17.660
<font color="#ffff54">And then...</font>

724
01:11:19.740 --> 01:11:21.400
<font color="#ffff54">What's their appetites?</font>

725
01:11:22.960 --> 01:11:24.740
<font color="#ffff54">Too much is never enough.</font>

726
01:12:24.980 --> 01:12:26.920
<font color="#ffff54">I don't...</font>

727
01:12:32.760 --> 01:12:33.460
<font color="#ffff54">oh</font>

728
01:12:41.140 --> 01:12:42.540
<font color="#ffff54">Gorillacus</font>

729
01:13:08.100 --> 01:13:09.480
<font color="#ffff54">They haven't come back yet.</font>

730
01:13:09.600 --> 01:13:10.060
<font color="#ffff54">None of them?</font>

731
01:13:10.240 --> 01:13:10.440
<font color="#ffff54">No.</font>

732
01:13:10.880 --> 01:13:11.500
<font color="#ffff54">Give me your dagger.</font>

733
01:13:15.380 --> 01:13:16.320
<font color="#ffff54">Stay with the boat.</font>

734
01:13:57.610 --> 01:13:59.130
<font color="#ffff54">Why don't you just come here?</font>

735
01:14:07.870 --> 01:14:09.230
<font color="#ffff54">Did you come from the sea?</font>

736
01:14:11.070 --> 01:14:12.030
<font color="#ffff54">Are you alone?</font>

737
01:14:17.660 --> 01:14:19.880
<font color="#ffff54">My pigs have taken a life into you.</font>

738
01:14:21.140 --> 01:14:22.040
<font color="#ffff54">Are you hungry?</font>

739
01:14:24.580 --> 01:14:26.200
<font color="#ffff54">Leave your weapons at the door.</font>

740
01:14:26.200 --> 01:14:28.380
<font color="#ffff54">Enjoy the hospitality of Zeus.</font>

741
01:14:30.120 --> 01:14:31.180
<font color="#ffff54">Grab a hog.</font>

742
01:14:31.320 --> 01:14:32.580
<font color="#ffff54">You can slaughter it for your dinner.</font>

743
01:14:57.960 --> 01:15:00.440
<font color="#ffff54">Whoever you are. you're clearly not a farmer.</font>

744
01:15:01.300 --> 01:15:01.440
<font color="#ffff54">Here.</font>

745
01:15:05.370 --> 01:15:06.690
<font color="#ffff54">That stew smells good.</font>

746
01:15:10.550 --> 01:15:11.910
<font color="#ffff54">That's enough for just us.</font>

747
01:15:13.270 --> 01:15:14.890
<font color="#ffff54">Who says it's just us?</font>

748
01:15:16.710 --> 01:15:17.970
<font color="#ffff54">Who else is here?</font>

749
01:15:18.530 --> 01:15:19.250
<font color="#ffff54">Who indeed.</font>

750
01:15:32.720 --> 01:15:34.400
<font color="#ffff54">You say you're all alone.</font>

751
01:15:34.780 --> 01:15:36.580
<font color="#ffff54">But no one comes here alone.</font>

752
01:15:37.780 --> 01:15:38.220
<font color="#ffff54">No?</font>

753
01:15:39.020 --> 01:15:41.380
<font color="#ffff54">You can only reach this spot by sea.</font>

754
01:15:42.060 --> 01:15:44.200
<font color="#ffff54">So. where are your shipmates?</font>

755
01:15:45.160 --> 01:15:46.280
<font color="#ffff54">I'm looking for them.</font>

756
01:15:47.880 --> 01:15:49.260
<font color="#ffff54">Anyone happen to come this way?</font>

757
01:15:52.400 --> 01:15:53.980
<font color="#ffff54">But you prepared all this food.</font>

758
01:15:54.240 --> 01:15:55.280
<font color="#ffff54">You're questioning me?</font>

759
01:15:55.660 --> 01:15:56.160
<font color="#ffff54">You?</font>

760
01:15:58.480 --> 01:16:00.580
<font color="#ffff54">A traveler who's clearly starving.</font>

761
01:16:00.860 --> 01:16:02.900
<font color="#ffff54">yet hasn't touched the food in front of him.</font>

762
01:16:03.380 --> 01:16:06.480
<font color="#ffff54">Claims to be a sailor. yet wears a great warrior's armor.</font>

763
01:16:07.540 --> 01:16:09.260
<font color="#ffff54">And who breaks Zeus's law</font>

764
01:16:09.980 --> 01:16:12.780
<font color="#ffff54">by bringing a dagger into his hostess's house.</font>

765
01:16:13.120 --> 01:16:14.340
<font color="#ffff54">You have sharp eyes.</font>

766
01:16:15.120 --> 01:16:16.380
<font color="#ffff54">Sharpened by the gods.</font>

767
01:16:17.300 --> 01:16:18.480
<font color="#ffff54">Do they grant you insights?</font>

768
01:16:19.800 --> 01:16:20.360
<font color="#ffff54">Truths.</font>

769
01:16:21.680 --> 01:16:22.240
<font color="#ffff54">Sometimes.</font>

770
01:16:23.280 --> 01:16:25.320
<font color="#ffff54">Would they tell you where I could find my men?</font>

771
01:16:26.100 --> 01:16:26.960
<font color="#ffff54">You're a man.</font>

772
01:16:27.440 --> 01:16:28.040
<font color="#ffff54">That's right.</font>

773
01:16:29.060 --> 01:16:29.780
<font color="#ffff54">They would.</font>

774
01:16:30.440 --> 01:16:31.380
<font color="#ffff54">And would you tell me?</font>

775
01:16:32.460 --> 01:16:33.020
<font color="#ffff54">Perhaps.</font>

776
01:16:35.100 --> 01:16:36.560
<font color="#ffff54">If you give me your dagger.</font>

777
01:16:45.480 --> 01:16:47.100
<font color="#ffff54">Why would I help a liar</font>

778
01:16:47.100 --> 01:16:48.680
<font color="#ffff54">who refuses my hospitality?</font>

779
01:16:59.360 --> 01:17:01.160
<font color="#ffff54">I remember here earlier.</font>

780
01:17:01.440 --> 01:17:02.380
<font color="#ffff54">Now they're not.</font>

781
01:17:08.980 --> 01:17:10.160
<font color="#ffff54">They moved on?</font>

782
01:17:10.920 --> 01:17:11.480
<font color="#ffff54">Yes.</font>

783
01:17:14.620 --> 01:17:15.720
<font color="#ffff54">Leaving their rings.</font>

784
01:17:24.100 --> 01:17:25.040
<font color="#ffff54">I wouldn't.</font>

785
01:17:27.020 --> 01:17:27.580
<font color="#ffff54">Don't.</font>

786
01:17:27.820 --> 01:17:29.600
<font color="#ffff54">I don't know who this crow is to you.</font>

787
01:17:29.600 --> 01:17:31.100
<font color="#ffff54">If you don't put that knife down.</font>

788
01:17:31.340 --> 01:17:32.840
<font color="#ffff54">I will throw out of it to find out.</font>

789
01:17:33.220 --> 01:17:34.060
<font color="#ffff54">Don't hurt her.</font>

790
01:17:34.360 --> 01:17:34.800
<font color="#ffff54">Family.</font>

791
01:17:37.340 --> 01:17:37.780
<font color="#ffff54">Mother.</font>

792
01:17:40.800 --> 01:17:41.580
<font color="#ffff54">Your sister.</font>

793
01:17:45.470 --> 01:17:48.170
<font color="#ffff54">You did this to her like you turned my men into pigs.</font>

794
01:17:48.370 --> 01:17:50.070
<font color="#ffff54">I didn't turn their men into anything.</font>

795
01:17:50.630 --> 01:17:51.390
<font color="#ffff54">Look at them.</font>

796
01:17:51.650 --> 01:17:52.670
<font color="#ffff54">This is who they are.</font>

797
01:17:52.770 --> 01:17:53.330
<font color="#ffff54">Look at them.</font>

798
01:17:53.990 --> 01:17:54.510
<font color="#ffff54">Base.</font>

799
01:17:54.930 --> 01:17:55.450
<font color="#ffff54">Base.</font>

800
01:17:55.450 --> 01:17:55.970
<font color="#ffff54">Disgusting.</font>

801
01:17:56.510 --> 01:17:58.630
<font color="#ffff54">Primal urges that you value in battle.</font>

802
01:17:59.010 --> 01:18:01.750
<font color="#ffff54">They've raped and pillaged across the world for you.</font>

803
01:18:01.990 --> 01:18:03.550
<font color="#ffff54">And you think that's against their nature?</font>

804
01:18:03.770 --> 01:18:05.810
<font color="#ffff54">You think they only did that because you ordered them to?</font>

805
01:18:06.170 --> 01:18:09.610
<font color="#ffff54">A true commander thinks his men's savagery is actually discipline.</font>

806
01:18:10.690 --> 01:18:12.350
<font color="#ffff54">You don't seem that deluded.</font>

807
01:18:12.350 --> 01:18:15.910
<font color="#ffff54">But you sent them to me here on my own.</font>

808
01:18:16.190 --> 01:18:19.990
<font color="#ffff54">A gang of filthy soldiers with empty bellies and hot blood.</font>

809
01:18:21.830 --> 01:18:24.790
<font color="#ffff54">You thought they'd respect me and my home?</font>

810
01:18:25.630 --> 01:18:26.850
<font color="#ffff54">Look at them.</font>

811
01:18:27.410 --> 01:18:28.550
<font color="#ffff54">Know your own men.</font>

812
01:18:29.630 --> 01:18:30.930
<font color="#ffff54">Did they hurt you?</font>

813
01:18:31.350 --> 01:18:32.530
<font color="#ffff54">They would have.</font>

814
01:18:33.290 --> 01:18:34.830
<font color="#ffff54">They just want to go home.</font>

815
01:18:38.380 --> 01:18:39.320
<font color="#ffff54">Let them.</font>

816
01:19:17.500 --> 01:19:18.900
<font color="#ffff54">Come back.</font>

817
01:19:27.290 --> 01:19:28.490
<font color="#ffff54">Come back.</font>

818
01:19:29.050 --> 01:19:33.040
<font color="#ffff54">I can't hear this guy.</font>

819
01:19:34.040 --> 01:19:34.460
<font color="#ffff54">Come back.</font>

820
01:19:39.180 --> 01:19:39.900
<font color="#ffff54">Odysseus.</font>

821
01:19:41.080 --> 01:19:41.800
<font color="#ffff54">Back to the ship.</font>

822
01:19:42.080 --> 01:19:43.740
<font color="#ffff54">Take all the food you can carry.</font>

823
01:19:44.460 --> 01:19:45.320
<font color="#ffff54">Leave the meat.</font>

824
01:19:45.920 --> 01:19:47.100
<font color="#ffff54">You're not going to let her live.</font>

825
01:19:47.200 --> 01:19:47.800
<font color="#ffff54">She's a witch.</font>

826
01:19:48.560 --> 01:19:49.740
<font color="#ffff54">Who gave her powers?</font>

827
01:19:50.140 --> 01:19:50.960
<font color="#ffff54">Your gods.</font>

828
01:19:51.720 --> 01:19:53.240
<font color="#ffff54">Fill the jugs and skins of the stream.</font>

829
01:19:53.460 --> 01:19:54.660
<font color="#ffff54">Be ready to sail at dawn.</font>

830
01:20:00.760 --> 01:20:02.040
<font color="#ffff54">Why leave her like this?</font>

831
01:20:02.740 --> 01:20:04.200
<font color="#ffff54">We got on better this way.</font>

832
01:20:05.940 --> 01:20:07.540
<font color="#ffff54">I'm sorry if we offended you.</font>

833
01:20:09.080 --> 01:20:10.800
<font color="#ffff54">We can't get back without your help.</font>

834
01:20:10.800 --> 01:20:13.160
<font color="#ffff54">We need to know the way to the trade routes.</font>

835
01:20:13.380 --> 01:20:14.460
<font color="#ffff54">You're too lost.</font>

836
01:20:15.020 --> 01:20:15.740
<font color="#ffff54">What do you mean?</font>

837
01:20:17.760 --> 01:20:20.520
<font color="#ffff54">Only blind Tiresias can tell you how to go home.</font>

838
01:20:20.840 --> 01:20:21.480
<font color="#ffff54">Tiresias?</font>

839
01:20:21.880 --> 01:20:22.560
<font color="#ffff54">In Hades.</font>

840
01:20:23.420 --> 01:20:26.480
<font color="#ffff54">Nobody sails into hell and comes back.</font>

841
01:20:26.820 --> 01:20:27.560
<font color="#ffff54">You will.</font>

842
01:20:28.800 --> 01:20:31.140
<font color="#ffff54">Head north into the twilight.</font>

843
01:20:36.810 --> 01:20:41.510
<font color="#ffff54">And head inland until a river of fire meets a river of ice.</font>

844
01:21:32.070 --> 01:21:33.670
<font color="#ffff54">There you must dig a trench.</font>

845
01:21:36.550 --> 01:21:38.750
<font color="#ffff54">And fill it with the blood of sacrifice.</font>

846
01:21:59.020 --> 01:22:00.240
<font color="#ffff54">Gather the dead.</font>

847
01:22:01.440 --> 01:22:03.460
<font color="#ffff54">And learn how you go home.</font>

848
01:22:05.580 --> 01:22:06.280
<font color="#ffff54">You.</font>

849
01:22:07.640 --> 01:22:08.880
<font color="#ffff54">Not your men.</font>

850
01:22:09.860 --> 01:22:10.900
<font color="#ffff54">You curse them?</font>

851
01:22:11.540 --> 01:22:12.700
<font color="#ffff54">Not a curse.</font>

852
01:22:13.640 --> 01:22:14.660
<font color="#ffff54">A truth.</font>

853
01:22:15.940 --> 01:22:18.500
<font color="#ffff54">Your men don't want you to defy the gods.</font>

854
01:22:19.940 --> 01:22:22.720
<font color="#ffff54">The gods say only you make it home.</font>

855
01:22:23.580 --> 01:22:25.320
<font color="#ffff54">Then I defy the gods.</font>

856
01:23:06.520 --> 01:23:07.560
<font color="#ffff54">Sennar.</font>

857
01:23:08.580 --> 01:23:09.480
<font color="#ffff54">It's Odysseus.</font>

858
01:23:14.800 --> 01:23:15.320
<font color="#ffff54">Sennar.</font>

859
01:23:16.500 --> 01:23:17.700
<font color="#ffff54">It's Odysseus.</font>

860
01:23:19.880 --> 01:23:21.960
<font color="#ffff54">Let him drink Odysseus.</font>

861
01:23:22.860 --> 01:23:24.540
<font color="#ffff54">Then you will hear his testings.</font>

862
01:23:39.710 --> 01:23:40.230
<font color="#ffff54">Odysseus.</font>

863
01:23:40.590 --> 01:23:41.110
<font color="#ffff54">Yes.</font>

864
01:23:42.030 --> 01:23:43.670
<font color="#ffff54">He lied to everyone.</font>

865
01:23:47.470 --> 01:23:48.950
<font color="#ffff54">Did you have to lie to me?</font>

866
01:23:50.550 --> 01:23:51.950
<font color="#ffff54">I needed you to believe.</font>

867
01:23:53.850 --> 01:23:55.450
<font color="#ffff54">Why did you have to volunteer?</font>

868
01:23:56.390 --> 01:23:58.150
<font color="#ffff54">Don't you remember how I came here?</font>

869
01:23:58.330 --> 01:24:01.050
<font color="#ffff54">I begged to take in Tendris' place.</font>

870
01:24:01.350 --> 01:24:02.350
<font color="#ffff54">He'd been called.</font>

871
01:24:03.010 --> 01:24:04.950
<font color="#ffff54">He offered money for your family.</font>

872
01:24:05.250 --> 01:24:06.130
<font color="#ffff54">If you take his place.</font>

873
01:24:06.990 --> 01:24:09.290
<font color="#ffff54">If the Trojans don't let me live.</font>

874
01:24:11.170 --> 01:24:12.690
<font color="#ffff54">If I never make it home.</font>

875
01:24:13.570 --> 01:24:15.070
<font color="#ffff54">Take this back to my father.</font>

876
01:24:16.630 --> 01:24:17.950
<font color="#ffff54">Tell him everything I did.</font>

877
01:24:21.650 --> 01:24:22.230
<font color="#ffff54">Odysseus.</font>

878
01:24:24.190 --> 01:24:26.350
<font color="#ffff54">Feel free to add some stuff.</font>

879
01:24:29.710 --> 01:24:31.850
<font color="#ffff54">You didn't trust me with the truth?</font>

880
01:24:33.850 --> 01:24:35.530
<font color="#ffff54">You knew I'd die for you.</font>

881
01:24:35.850 --> 01:24:37.350
<font color="#ffff54">Dying men tell the truth.</font>

882
01:24:37.350 --> 01:24:38.450
<font color="#ffff54">I needed you to believe.</font>

883
01:24:38.970 --> 01:24:41.530
<font color="#ffff54">I died for your lie on that beach.</font>

884
01:24:42.390 --> 01:24:43.190
<font color="#ffff54">I know.</font>

885
01:24:43.450 --> 01:24:44.850
<font color="#ffff54">I was there with you.</font>

886
01:24:45.170 --> 01:24:48.050
<font color="#ffff54">I heard you repeat the lie with your dying breath.</font>

887
01:24:48.250 --> 01:24:49.510
<font color="#ffff54">Winning us the war.</font>

888
01:24:50.030 --> 01:24:50.990
<font color="#ffff54">I was right there.</font>

889
01:24:51.270 --> 01:24:51.950
<font color="#ffff54">Inches from you.</font>

890
01:24:52.110 --> 01:24:52.730
<font color="#ffff54">Smelling your blood.</font>

891
01:24:52.890 --> 01:24:54.590
<font color="#ffff54">What comfort could that give me?</font>

892
01:24:55.870 --> 01:24:58.170
<font color="#ffff54">Not knowing you were inside that horse.</font>

893
01:24:58.410 --> 01:24:59.990
<font color="#ffff54">Until the dead told me.</font>

894
01:25:01.050 --> 01:25:01.770
<font color="#ffff54">Which dead?</font>

895
01:25:02.290 --> 01:25:05.550
<font color="#ffff54">A lot of veterans of your campaigns walk these shores.</font>

896
01:25:07.890 --> 01:25:10.690
<font color="#ffff54">The dead meet to lament the living.</font>

897
01:25:11.090 --> 01:25:12.830
<font color="#ffff54">And greet the newly dead.</font>

898
01:25:13.610 --> 01:25:16.210
<font color="#ffff54">My father was the first shade to find me.</font>

899
01:25:16.590 --> 01:25:17.550
<font color="#ffff54">To comfort you.</font>

900
01:25:18.210 --> 01:25:19.450
<font color="#ffff54">Shades don't comfort.</font>

901
01:25:19.450 --> 01:25:23.670
<font color="#ffff54">They want word of the living who wronged them.</font>

902
01:25:24.370 --> 01:25:26.790
<font color="#ffff54">My father had died in poverty.</font>

903
01:25:27.230 --> 01:25:27.930
<font color="#ffff54">Alone.</font>

904
01:25:28.390 --> 01:25:31.590
<font color="#ffff54">Begging for scraps from people like Antinous.</font>

905
01:25:32.170 --> 01:25:33.550
<font color="#ffff54">Antinous cheated you?</font>

906
01:25:34.150 --> 01:25:36.350
<font color="#ffff54">As he's no doubt cheating you.</font>

907
01:25:36.770 --> 01:25:37.310
<font color="#ffff54">How?</font>

908
01:25:37.590 --> 01:25:40.270
<font color="#ffff54">Who's in Ithaca looking after your wife and son?</font>

909
01:25:40.570 --> 01:25:42.050
<font color="#ffff54">My wife is of no concern.</font>

910
01:25:43.450 --> 01:25:46.150
<font color="#ffff54">Talk to Agamemnon about homecomings.</font>

911
01:25:47.390 --> 01:25:48.390
<font color="#ffff54">Agamemnon's here.</font>

912
01:25:51.430 --> 01:25:53.750
<font color="#ffff54">You buried me at Troy with respect.</font>

913
01:25:53.930 --> 01:25:54.890
<font color="#ffff54">Thank you.</font>

914
01:25:55.550 --> 01:25:57.790
<font color="#ffff54">But spare a thought for those you didn't.</font>

915
01:25:58.110 --> 01:25:59.770
<font color="#ffff54">It's not always possible.</font>

916
01:26:00.610 --> 01:26:01.870
<font color="#ffff54">When you get home.</font>

917
01:26:02.930 --> 01:26:04.030
<font color="#ffff54">Take a ship.</font>

918
01:26:04.550 --> 01:26:06.970
<font color="#ffff54">Head into the unknown west till you find land.</font>

919
01:26:07.350 --> 01:26:08.010
<font color="#ffff54">And there.</font>

920
01:26:08.210 --> 01:26:09.110
<font color="#ffff54">Give sacrifice.</font>

921
01:26:09.630 --> 01:26:10.890
<font color="#ffff54">And honor your men.</font>

922
01:26:13.110 --> 01:26:14.690
<font color="#ffff54">Do you still have the lot?</font>

923
01:26:18.240 --> 01:26:19.120
<font color="#ffff54">Of course.</font>

924
01:26:20.140 --> 01:26:21.240
<font color="#ffff54">If you make it home.</font>

925
01:26:21.500 --> 01:26:23.280
<font color="#ffff54">Give Antinous back his shame.</font>

926
01:26:23.800 --> 01:26:24.300
<font color="#ffff54">I will.</font>

927
01:26:35.800 --> 01:26:36.560
<font color="#ffff54">My lord.</font>

928
01:26:48.880 --> 01:26:49.400
<font color="#ffff54">Odysseus.</font>

929
01:26:50.440 --> 01:26:51.460
<font color="#ffff54">How are you here?</font>

930
01:26:52.240 --> 01:26:54.160
<font color="#ffff54">We won the war you headed for home.</font>

931
01:26:55.260 --> 01:26:55.780
<font color="#ffff54">Odysseus.</font>

932
01:26:56.400 --> 01:26:58.200
<font color="#ffff54">The most brilliant of all my generals.</font>

933
01:26:59.580 --> 01:27:01.560
<font color="#ffff54">He would never be snared as I was.</font>

934
01:27:01.680 --> 01:27:02.660
<font color="#ffff54">Were you cast adrift?</font>

935
01:27:02.860 --> 01:27:03.300
<font color="#ffff54">Like us?</font>

936
01:27:03.300 --> 01:27:04.600
<font color="#ffff54">No.</font>

937
01:27:05.040 --> 01:27:06.860
<font color="#ffff54">My misfortune was to make it home.</font>

938
01:27:07.940 --> 01:27:10.280
<font color="#ffff54">To be welcomed by my beautiful wife.</font>

939
01:27:16.680 --> 01:27:17.340
<font color="#ffff54">Bathed.</font>

940
01:27:20.160 --> 01:27:20.820
<font color="#ffff54">Anointed.</font>

941
01:27:23.380 --> 01:27:24.540
<font color="#ffff54">Made soft.</font>

942
01:27:25.780 --> 01:27:27.480
<font color="#ffff54">To learn the hardest lesson.</font>

943
01:27:28.160 --> 01:27:30.740
<font color="#ffff54">That I'd left a poison in her heart years before.</font>

944
01:27:33.460 --> 01:27:35.020
<font color="#ffff54">Good part of her heart had gone.</font>

945
01:27:36.880 --> 01:27:37.440
<font color="#ffff54">Ah!</font>

946
01:27:38.560 --> 01:27:38.880
<font color="#ffff54">Ah!</font>

947
01:27:38.880 --> 01:27:39.220
<font color="#ffff54">Ah!</font>

948
01:27:39.440 --> 01:27:39.560
<font color="#ffff54">Ah!</font>

949
01:27:40.060 --> 01:27:40.420
<font color="#ffff54">Oh. no.</font>

950
01:27:41.520 --> 01:27:44.220
<font color="#ffff54">She and her lover had plotted my murder for years.</font>

951
01:27:46.160 --> 01:27:46.720
<font color="#ffff54">Odysseus.</font>

952
01:27:47.880 --> 01:27:48.440
<font color="#ffff54">Yes?</font>

953
01:27:49.280 --> 01:27:50.580
<font color="#ffff54">My son. Orestes.</font>

954
01:27:51.140 --> 01:27:52.340
<font color="#ffff54">Did he avenge me?</font>

955
01:27:52.920 --> 01:27:54.060
<font color="#ffff54">My lord. how could I know?</font>

956
01:27:55.180 --> 01:27:56.680
<font color="#ffff54">I'm still trying to get home.</font>

957
01:27:57.960 --> 01:27:59.200
<font color="#ffff54">Don't make my mistake.</font>

958
01:28:00.620 --> 01:28:03.460
<font color="#ffff54">Don't walk in the front door expecting garlands and praise.</font>

959
01:28:04.420 --> 01:28:05.420
<font color="#ffff54">Come in disguise.</font>

960
01:28:06.500 --> 01:28:07.460
<font color="#ffff54">Take your time.</font>

961
01:28:08.800 --> 01:28:09.280
<font color="#ffff54">Assess.</font>

962
01:28:16.730 --> 01:28:17.570
<font color="#ffff54">Do you see?</font>

963
01:28:19.550 --> 01:28:20.950
<font color="#ffff54">I know what I have to do.</font>

964
01:28:21.470 --> 01:28:23.030
<font color="#ffff54">Some of what you have to do.</font>

965
01:28:23.210 --> 01:28:25.210
<font color="#ffff54">My prophecy is not for their ears.</font>

966
01:28:26.810 --> 01:28:27.790
<font color="#ffff54">Back to the ship.</font>

967
01:28:30.070 --> 01:28:31.210
<font color="#ffff54">Sail southwest.</font>

968
01:28:31.630 --> 01:28:32.650
<font color="#ffff54">Pass the sirens.</font>

969
01:28:33.870 --> 01:28:36.470
<font color="#ffff54">Their song lures your men onto the rocks.</font>

970
01:28:36.690 --> 01:28:37.450
<font color="#ffff54">They all die.</font>

971
01:28:37.790 --> 01:28:38.830
<font color="#ffff54">I won't let that happen.</font>

972
01:28:39.390 --> 01:28:40.730
<font color="#ffff54">I'll block their ears.</font>

973
01:28:40.950 --> 01:28:41.550
<font color="#ffff54">With wax.</font>

974
01:28:41.990 --> 01:28:43.190
<font color="#ffff54">Pass the sirens.</font>

975
01:28:43.470 --> 01:28:47.170
<font color="#ffff54">You choose between the whirlpool Charybdis and the monster Scylla.</font>

976
01:28:47.490 --> 01:28:50.050
<font color="#ffff54">The whirlpool in the sea takes all of your lives.</font>

977
01:28:50.230 --> 01:28:51.310
<font color="#ffff54">The monster in the cliffs?</font>

978
01:28:51.470 --> 01:28:52.170
<font color="#ffff54">Only six.</font>

979
01:28:52.550 --> 01:28:56.950
<font color="#ffff54">But your determination to not sacrifice any more lives kills all of them.</font>

980
01:28:57.810 --> 01:28:59.050
<font color="#ffff54">I'll do what I have to.</font>

981
01:28:59.430 --> 01:28:59.930
<font color="#ffff54">At the end.</font>

982
01:29:00.130 --> 01:29:05.430
<font color="#ffff54">When starvation and mutiny threaten. they demand to land where the sun god grazes his cattle.</font>

983
01:29:05.830 --> 01:29:07.690
<font color="#ffff54">They slaughter Apollo's herd.</font>

984
01:29:09.090 --> 01:29:10.670
<font color="#ffff54">Zeus kills them for it.</font>

985
01:29:11.090 --> 01:29:11.990
<font color="#ffff54">Do you see?</font>

986
01:29:13.070 --> 01:29:14.150
<font color="#ffff54">I'll stop them.</font>

987
01:29:14.550 --> 01:29:18.070
<font color="#ffff54">Why do you value these men's lives more than those you've already lost?</font>

988
01:29:18.070 --> 01:29:19.990
<font color="#ffff54">I can still save them from the gods.</font>

989
01:29:21.010 --> 01:29:22.490
<font color="#ffff54">But not from themselves.</font>

990
01:29:25.390 --> 01:29:26.430
<font color="#ffff54">What is that?</font>

991
01:29:26.910 --> 01:29:27.990
<font color="#ffff54">Your unburied crew.</font>

992
01:29:31.770 --> 01:29:33.830
<font color="#ffff54">Demanding you share their dishonor.</font>

993
01:29:35.870 --> 01:29:36.950
<font color="#ffff54">Let's go!</font>

994
01:30:47.900 --> 01:30:49.860
<font color="#ffff54">We rode out of hell.</font>

995
01:30:51.400 --> 01:30:53.740
<font color="#ffff54">Leaving so many fallen comrades.</font>

996
01:30:54.440 --> 01:30:56.360
<font color="#ffff54">I have to save the rest.</font>

997
01:30:57.160 --> 01:30:58.560
<font color="#ffff54">What's happened to them?</font>

998
01:30:59.060 --> 01:31:00.720
<font color="#ffff54">Did they leave me here?</font>

999
01:31:01.040 --> 01:31:02.220
<font color="#ffff54">Are they coming back?</font>

1000
01:31:04.460 --> 01:31:06.160
<font color="#ffff54">Did you do something to them?</font>

1001
01:31:07.740 --> 01:31:09.320
<font color="#ffff54">Did you do something to them?</font>

1002
01:31:09.600 --> 01:31:10.180
<font color="#ffff54">I hope so.</font>

1003
01:31:11.160 --> 01:31:13.140
<font color="#ffff54">You told me not to eat the lotus flower.</font>

1004
01:31:13.420 --> 01:31:14.200
<font color="#ffff54">Just tonight.</font>

1005
01:31:15.160 --> 01:31:16.580
<font color="#ffff54">So you can get some sleep.</font>

1006
01:31:19.950 --> 01:31:23.170
<font color="#ffff54">And tomorrow. when you're ready. you'll remember.</font>

1007
01:31:26.390 --> 01:31:27.970
<font color="#ffff54">You'll remember your crew.</font>

1008
01:31:28.810 --> 01:31:29.950
<font color="#ffff54">And your family.</font>

1009
01:31:30.310 --> 01:31:30.910
<font color="#ffff54">Family?</font>

1010
01:31:32.990 --> 01:31:33.950
<font color="#ffff54">A wife?</font>

1011
01:31:35.970 --> 01:31:37.350
<font color="#ffff54">Do I have a wife?</font>

1012
01:31:43.050 --> 01:31:44.630
<font color="#ffff54">So I'm a lanthal.</font>

1013
01:31:45.390 --> 01:31:46.490
<font color="#ffff54">Strangers don't come in here.</font>

1014
01:31:47.030 --> 01:31:51.390
<font color="#ffff54">Screen or no screen. after three years of feasting together. we're far from strangers. Penelope.</font>

1015
01:31:51.390 --> 01:31:54.590
<font color="#ffff54">Are you trying to marry me or ruin my reputation?</font>

1016
01:31:55.010 --> 01:31:56.170
<font color="#ffff54">Melanthal can be discreet.</font>

1017
01:31:56.510 --> 01:31:59.930
<font color="#ffff54">I'm actually here out of concern for your reputation.</font>

1018
01:32:00.390 --> 01:32:00.830
<font color="#ffff54">Oh?</font>

1019
01:32:01.310 --> 01:32:02.930
<font color="#ffff54">Everyone sees how hard you work.</font>

1020
01:32:03.190 --> 01:32:05.390
<font color="#ffff54">Slow. steady progress.</font>

1021
01:32:06.030 --> 01:32:06.250
<font color="#ffff54">Hmm.</font>

1022
01:32:06.950 --> 01:32:09.050
<font color="#ffff54">But every night. you've been unraveling that work.</font>

1023
01:32:14.820 --> 01:32:15.680
<font color="#ffff54">Leave us.</font>

1024
01:32:17.680 --> 01:32:21.480
<font color="#ffff54">You can't expect her to be loyal to a master she never even knew.</font>

1025
01:32:21.720 --> 01:32:23.500
<font color="#ffff54">I expect her to be loyal to me.</font>

1026
01:32:23.780 --> 01:32:24.560
<font color="#ffff54">I mean. she will be.</font>

1027
01:32:24.560 --> 01:32:25.860
<font color="#ffff54">And you're married to me.</font>

1028
01:32:28.060 --> 01:32:30.560
<font color="#ffff54">Slaves have no choice but to be loyal to the future.</font>

1029
01:32:30.920 --> 01:32:33.140
<font color="#ffff54">And this is a household waiting for a master.</font>

1030
01:32:33.420 --> 01:32:35.600
<font color="#ffff54">Just as Ithaca is a kingdom waiting for a king.</font>

1031
01:32:38.460 --> 01:32:39.860
<font color="#ffff54">Ithaca's king is coming back.</font>

1032
01:32:40.400 --> 01:32:41.220
<font color="#ffff54">No. he's not.</font>

1033
01:32:43.140 --> 01:32:46.000
<font color="#ffff54">Did you know that as a boy. I tried to go with him to Troy?</font>

1034
01:32:47.160 --> 01:32:48.400
<font color="#ffff54">He never told me that.</font>

1035
01:32:50.180 --> 01:32:51.420
<font color="#ffff54">Dizzy's refused to let me.</font>

1036
01:32:51.680 --> 01:32:54.700
<font color="#ffff54">He knew that Ithaca needed a future without him.</font>

1037
01:33:01.480 --> 01:33:03.400
<font color="#ffff54">And he saw me as part of that future.</font>

1038
01:33:08.150 --> 01:33:12.950
<font color="#ffff54">I'll never tell other suitors about your deception.</font>

1039
01:33:15.830 --> 01:33:17.050
<font color="#ffff54">Finish your weaving.</font>

1040
01:33:19.090 --> 01:33:20.390
<font color="#ffff54">It's time to let him go.</font>

1041
01:33:29.910 --> 01:33:32.450
<font color="#ffff54">Why would you want to marry someone who loves someone else?</font>

1042
01:33:35.470 --> 01:33:40.110
<font color="#ffff54">Your loyalty to a disuse is one of your finest qualities.</font>

1043
01:33:43.470 --> 01:33:44.650
<font color="#ffff54">I love you.</font>

1044
01:33:45.450 --> 01:33:48.710
<font color="#ffff54">I want you to choose me and end all this.</font>

1045
01:33:50.130 --> 01:33:52.630
<font color="#ffff54">You can't tell me you're not tired.</font>

1046
01:33:58.430 --> 01:34:05.570
<font color="#ffff54">You've done your duty year after year after year.</font>

1047
01:34:08.450 --> 01:34:09.990
<font color="#ffff54">It's time to think of yourself.</font>

1048
01:34:11.890 --> 01:34:13.170
<font color="#ffff54">It's time to live again.</font>

1049
01:34:18.800 --> 01:34:20.380
<font color="#ffff54">It's what a disuse would have wanted.</font>

1050
01:34:27.380 --> 01:34:29.120
<font color="#ffff54">I'll take care of all your needs.</font>

1051
01:34:37.750 --> 01:34:38.890
<font color="#ffff54">And my son.</font>

1052
01:34:40.830 --> 01:34:41.890
<font color="#ffff54">Withthrown as he is.</font>

1053
01:34:42.450 --> 01:34:43.430
<font color="#ffff54">He's the heir.</font>

1054
01:34:45.990 --> 01:34:47.710
<font color="#ffff54">Unless we have a child of our own.</font>

1055
01:34:58.040 --> 01:34:59.180
<font color="#ffff54">Where is Telemachus?</font>

1056
01:35:01.180 --> 01:35:02.340
<font color="#ffff54">He's gone inland.</font>

1057
01:35:02.700 --> 01:35:03.920
<font color="#ffff54">To visit his grandfather.</font>

1058
01:35:29.770 --> 01:35:31.350
<font color="#ffff54">He's gone for years of his father.</font>

1059
01:35:32.310 --> 01:35:32.890
<font color="#ffff54">Where?</font>

1060
01:35:33.510 --> 01:35:34.710
<font color="#ffff54">He's gone to Sparta.</font>

1061
01:35:34.970 --> 01:35:35.850
<font color="#ffff54">To Menelaus.</font>

1062
01:35:37.130 --> 01:35:38.230
<font color="#ffff54">Well. should we go there?</font>

1063
01:35:39.770 --> 01:35:40.250
<font color="#ffff54">No.</font>

1064
01:35:42.050 --> 01:35:43.510
<font color="#ffff54">To move out. Melanthius.</font>

1065
01:35:43.670 --> 01:35:44.930
<font color="#ffff54">I told you you're a coward.</font>

1066
01:35:46.270 --> 01:35:47.330
<font color="#ffff54">He was listening.</font>

1067
01:35:47.330 --> 01:35:47.890
<font color="#ffff54">No. no.</font>

1068
01:35:48.150 --> 01:35:49.050
<font color="#ffff54">No. no.</font>

1069
01:35:51.190 --> 01:35:52.590
<font color="#ffff54">I was coming for Argus.</font>

1070
01:35:53.890 --> 01:35:55.590
<font color="#ffff54">I told you that dog stays there.</font>

1071
01:35:55.730 --> 01:35:56.650
<font color="#ffff54">Go back to the farm.</font>

1072
01:35:56.870 --> 01:35:58.510
<font color="#ffff54">When you need your pigs. we'll send Melanthius.</font>

1073
01:35:59.610 --> 01:36:01.950
<font color="#ffff54">You're no longer welcome to this palace. old man.</font>

1074
01:36:02.210 --> 01:36:03.690
<font color="#ffff54">I answered to my mistress.</font>

1075
01:36:06.250 --> 01:36:07.530
<font color="#ffff54">Does she even know your name?</font>

1076
01:36:09.090 --> 01:36:09.750
<font color="#ffff54">Now go.</font>

1077
01:36:11.230 --> 01:36:14.310
<font color="#ffff54">Telemachus will have to come back by the temple at Pylos.</font>

1078
01:36:14.910 --> 01:36:16.250
<font color="#ffff54">Take your man away from there.</font>

1079
01:36:17.090 --> 01:36:18.930
<font color="#ffff54">Well. so you can stay and try and charm the queen.</font>

1080
01:36:18.930 --> 01:36:20.030
<font color="#ffff54">I don't think so.</font>

1081
01:36:20.870 --> 01:36:22.490
<font color="#ffff54">He needs to die on that road.</font>

1082
01:36:23.150 --> 01:36:24.110
<font color="#ffff54">And Argus has a plan.</font>

1083
01:36:25.430 --> 01:36:25.990
<font color="#ffff54">Argus!</font>

1084
01:36:28.350 --> 01:36:30.310
<font color="#ffff54">I need everyone in this party dead.</font>

1085
01:36:30.590 --> 01:36:31.370
<font color="#ffff54">In a ditch.</font>

1086
01:36:31.690 --> 01:36:32.610
<font color="#ffff54">Throats open.</font>

1087
01:36:32.610 --> 01:36:37.210
<font color="#ffff54">Then Telemachus and his men will be ready for the bandits who work the road between here and Pylos.</font>

1088
01:36:38.350 --> 01:36:41.610
<font color="#ffff54">But if some of them took the temple from the priests before they arrived...</font>

1089
01:36:43.250 --> 01:36:45.170
<font color="#ffff54">Then bring me part of Telemachus' proof.</font>

1090
01:36:46.870 --> 01:36:47.650
<font color="#ffff54">His nose.</font>

1091
01:36:48.490 --> 01:36:50.170
<font color="#ffff54">Would you know him only by his nose?</font>

1092
01:36:53.830 --> 01:36:54.730
<font color="#ffff54">His ears. too.</font>

1093
01:37:00.140 --> 01:37:01.300
<font color="#ffff54">Who taught you?</font>

1094
01:37:01.860 --> 01:37:03.140
<font color="#ffff54">My father's swineherd.</font>

1095
01:37:03.720 --> 01:37:04.440
<font color="#ffff54">Swineherd.</font>

1096
01:37:04.940 --> 01:37:06.220
<font color="#ffff54">His most loyal servant.</font>

1097
01:37:07.100 --> 01:37:09.700
<font color="#ffff54">Odysseus left his most loyal servant behind.</font>

1098
01:37:10.060 --> 01:37:11.440
<font color="#ffff54">He always was the smartest.</font>

1099
01:37:12.620 --> 01:37:14.580
<font color="#ffff54">Only one Agamemnon ever listened to.</font>

1100
01:37:15.460 --> 01:37:16.880
<font color="#ffff54">Should have listened harder.</font>

1101
01:37:17.740 --> 01:37:19.160
<font color="#ffff54">Can I ask what happened to your brother?</font>

1102
01:37:19.440 --> 01:37:20.700
<font color="#ffff54">His wife betrayed him.</font>

1103
01:37:21.080 --> 01:37:21.680
<font color="#ffff54">Murdered him.</font>

1104
01:37:22.520 --> 01:37:23.640
<font color="#ffff54">What did you do to them?</font>

1105
01:37:23.900 --> 01:37:24.780
<font color="#ffff54">His son. Orestes.</font>

1106
01:37:24.960 --> 01:37:25.860
<font color="#ffff54">He killed them both.</font>

1107
01:37:26.680 --> 01:37:27.940
<font color="#ffff54">But he killed his own mother?</font>

1108
01:37:29.200 --> 01:37:30.500
<font color="#ffff54">He avenged his father.</font>

1109
01:37:31.360 --> 01:37:32.520
<font color="#ffff54">But you don't have to worry.</font>

1110
01:37:32.860 --> 01:37:35.300
<font color="#ffff54">Your mother has nothing in common with Clytemnestra.</font>

1111
01:37:35.960 --> 01:37:36.680
<font color="#ffff54">Maybe not.</font>

1112
01:37:37.000 --> 01:37:39.880
<font color="#ffff54">But the suitors have convinced the elders it's time she remarried.</font>

1113
01:37:40.160 --> 01:37:40.420
<font color="#ffff54">Yeah.</font>

1114
01:37:40.940 --> 01:37:42.660
<font color="#ffff54">It's not a good time for an empty throne.</font>

1115
01:37:43.400 --> 01:37:44.380
<font color="#ffff54">Heard the stories.</font>

1116
01:37:44.620 --> 01:37:45.460
<font color="#ffff54">People from the sea.</font>

1117
01:37:45.960 --> 01:37:46.840
<font color="#ffff54">Have you been raided?</font>

1118
01:37:47.000 --> 01:37:49.340
<font color="#ffff54">Not yet. but the attacks. they do seem closer.</font>

1119
01:37:49.960 --> 01:37:50.720
<font color="#ffff54">Sparta's ready.</font>

1120
01:37:50.720 --> 01:37:51.860
<font color="#ffff54">What about Ithaca?</font>

1121
01:37:52.580 --> 01:37:54.800
<font color="#ffff54">She'll be able to raise an army. defend herself.</font>

1122
01:37:55.100 --> 01:37:56.400
<font color="#ffff54">Someone's got to take the throne.</font>

1123
01:37:56.620 --> 01:37:58.680
<font color="#ffff54">Then the battle is there. not here. son.</font>

1124
01:37:59.580 --> 01:38:00.980
<font color="#ffff54">You've run from the problem.</font>

1125
01:38:02.140 --> 01:38:04.480
<font color="#ffff54">Left your mother. the mercy of the suitors.</font>

1126
01:38:05.840 --> 01:38:07.400
<font color="#ffff54">Should I hire mercenaries?</font>

1127
01:38:07.780 --> 01:38:09.180
<font color="#ffff54">Go back and kill them all?</font>

1128
01:38:10.140 --> 01:38:12.620
<font color="#ffff54">Murder rich and powerful guests in your own home.</font>

1129
01:38:12.920 --> 01:38:14.040
<font color="#ffff54">You'll be exiled.</font>

1130
01:38:15.000 --> 01:38:15.720
<font color="#ffff54">What then?</font>

1131
01:38:16.360 --> 01:38:18.860
<font color="#ffff54">You must evict them without violating Zeus' law.</font>

1132
01:38:21.140 --> 01:38:22.600
<font color="#ffff54">I have to take the throne.</font>

1133
01:38:23.840 --> 01:38:25.660
<font color="#ffff54">I have to know if Odysseus is alive.</font>

1134
01:38:26.440 --> 01:38:28.900
<font color="#ffff54">This has nothing to do with a father you've never known.</font>

1135
01:38:29.800 --> 01:38:31.180
<font color="#ffff54">You have to lead. son.</font>

1136
01:38:31.700 --> 01:38:33.380
<font color="#ffff54">No matter what's happened to Odysseus.</font>

1137
01:38:47.460 --> 01:38:48.800
<font color="#ffff54">You need to remember.</font>

1138
01:38:49.180 --> 01:38:50.000
<font color="#ffff54">No. I don't.</font>

1139
01:38:51.020 --> 01:38:52.420
<font color="#ffff54">I don't need to know the truth.</font>

1140
01:38:52.420 --> 01:38:53.880
<font color="#ffff54">Odysseus. I'm happy here with you.</font>

1141
01:38:55.940 --> 01:39:00.180
<font color="#ffff54">And why are you gathering the bones of your old ship to make a raft?</font>

1142
01:39:02.660 --> 01:39:03.900
<font color="#ffff54">Remember your crew.</font>

1143
01:39:05.440 --> 01:39:06.500
<font color="#ffff54">Your journey.</font>

1144
01:39:10.860 --> 01:39:12.800
<font color="#ffff54">I heard the song of the sirens.</font>

1145
01:39:22.660 --> 01:39:24.260
<font color="#ffff54">Put the wax in the men's ears.</font>

1146
01:39:25.460 --> 01:39:26.220
<font color="#ffff54">None for me.</font>

1147
01:39:26.500 --> 01:39:27.280
<font color="#ffff54">Tie me to the mast.</font>

1148
01:39:27.740 --> 01:39:28.080
<font color="#ffff54">Why?</font>

1149
01:39:28.480 --> 01:39:29.940
<font color="#ffff54">I want to hear the siren song.</font>

1150
01:39:30.500 --> 01:39:30.720
<font color="#ffff54">No.</font>

1151
01:39:31.620 --> 01:39:32.600
<font color="#ffff54">That's a bad idea.</font>

1152
01:39:33.140 --> 01:39:34.680
<font color="#ffff54">No one's ever heard the song and lived.</font>

1153
01:39:34.920 --> 01:39:35.960
<font color="#ffff54">That's why it's a good idea.</font>

1154
01:39:36.160 --> 01:39:36.840
<font color="#ffff54">I'll be the first.</font>

1155
01:39:37.900 --> 01:39:42.020
<font color="#ffff54">No matter how hard I plead. do not untie me until we're well clear.</font>

1156
01:39:43.220 --> 01:39:44.320
<font color="#ffff54">Check the men's ears.</font>

1157
01:39:45.600 --> 01:39:47.220
<font color="#ffff54">A week's rations for the first.</font>

1158
01:39:47.380 --> 01:39:47.960
<font color="#ffff54">Yes. sir.</font>

1159
01:40:46.580 --> 01:40:48.000
<font color="#ffff54">What was the siren song?</font>

1160
01:40:49.520 --> 01:40:51.140
<font color="#ffff54">All the things he wanted to be.</font>

1161
01:40:53.240 --> 01:40:55.780
<font color="#ffff54">Then. all the things he wished he'd never wished for.</font>

1162
01:41:13.840 --> 01:41:16.780
<font color="#ffff54">It was the delicious itch you go to scratch.</font>

1163
01:41:17.980 --> 01:41:20.700
<font color="#ffff54">They find it's under the skin and you can't reach it.</font>

1164
01:41:23.100 --> 01:41:25.660
<font color="#ffff54">So the delicious itch becomes unbearable.</font>

1165
01:41:30.060 --> 01:41:31.920
<font color="#ffff54">Told you what you most want</font>

1166
01:41:34.020 --> 01:41:35.960
<font color="#ffff54">is what you most can't have.</font>

1167
01:41:39.500 --> 01:41:41.420
<font color="#ffff54">And what you most can't have</font>

1168
01:41:42.540 --> 01:41:44.260
<font color="#ffff54">is what you already had</font>

1169
01:41:45.260 --> 01:41:46.260
<font color="#ffff54">and lost.</font>

1170
01:41:54.900 --> 01:41:56.820
<font color="#ffff54">It was the song of all the promises</font>

1171
01:41:56.820 --> 01:41:57.820
<font color="#ffff54">I failed to keep.</font>

1172
01:42:02.730 --> 01:42:03.690
<font color="#ffff54">And it told me</font>

1173
01:42:03.690 --> 01:42:05.030
<font color="#ffff54">I don't really want to go home.</font>

1174
01:42:10.240 --> 01:42:11.640
<font color="#ffff54">I want her ahead!</font>

1175
01:42:14.460 --> 01:42:14.940
<font color="#ffff54">Charybdis.</font>

1176
01:42:16.660 --> 01:42:18.220
<font color="#ffff54">A monstrous whirlpool.</font>

1177
01:42:21.240 --> 01:42:22.080
<font color="#ffff54">Horses of sails!</font>

1178
01:42:22.560 --> 01:42:23.240
<font color="#ffff54">Come on. let's go!</font>

1179
01:42:23.880 --> 01:42:24.580
<font color="#ffff54">It's a wind!</font>

1180
01:42:24.740 --> 01:42:25.200
<font color="#ffff54">Let's go!</font>

1181
01:42:25.800 --> 01:42:26.940
<font color="#ffff54">Can we head out to sea?</font>

1182
01:42:27.160 --> 01:42:28.260
<font color="#ffff54">It's already got us!</font>

1183
01:42:30.460 --> 01:42:31.480
<font color="#ffff54">Get in the boat!</font>

1184
01:42:32.160 --> 01:42:33.000
<font color="#ffff54">Get in the boat!</font>

1185
01:42:33.520 --> 01:42:33.720
<font color="#ffff54">Move it!</font>

1186
01:42:35.160 --> 01:42:36.400
<font color="#ffff54">We might make that canyon.</font>

1187
01:42:36.560 --> 01:42:37.300
<font color="#ffff54">It's too narrow.</font>

1188
01:42:37.860 --> 01:42:39.060
<font color="#ffff54">Make for the whirlpool.</font>

1189
01:42:39.320 --> 01:42:41.040
<font color="#ffff54">If you steer down the slope.</font>

1190
01:42:41.060 --> 01:42:42.020
<font color="#ffff54">we can make enough way</font>

1191
01:42:42.020 --> 01:42:43.300
<font color="#ffff54">to shoot out the other side.</font>

1192
01:42:43.500 --> 01:42:44.340
<font color="#ffff54">Don't be afraid.</font>

1193
01:42:44.500 --> 01:42:45.000
<font color="#ffff54">We can do it.</font>

1194
01:42:45.000 --> 01:42:45.040
<font color="#ffff54">We can do it.</font>

1195
01:42:45.040 --> 01:42:47.600
<font color="#ffff54">We can do it.</font>

1196
01:42:50.160 --> 01:42:50.720
<font color="#ffff54">No.</font>

1197
01:42:51.280 --> 01:42:51.640
<font color="#ffff54">No!</font>

1198
01:42:52.280 --> 01:42:53.500
<font color="#ffff54">We're making for the channel.</font>

1199
01:42:54.580 --> 01:42:55.560
<font color="#ffff54">We're making for the channel!</font>

1200
01:42:58.620 --> 01:42:59.820
<font color="#ffff54">Get the oars in!</font>

1201
01:42:59.820 --> 01:43:00.180
<font color="#ffff54">Get the oars in!</font>

1202
01:43:00.760 --> 01:43:01.260
<font color="#ffff54">Get the oars in!</font>

1203
01:43:01.260 --> 01:43:03.240
<font color="#ffff54">Governors. prepare to hold water!</font>

1204
01:43:03.240 --> 01:43:41.670
<font color="#ffff54">It's time to travel!</font>

1205
01:44:09.210 --> 01:44:10.650
<font color="#ffff54">You did!</font>

1206
01:44:11.050 --> 01:44:12.350
<font color="#ffff54">We did!</font>

1207
01:44:12.950 --> 01:44:13.210
<font color="#ffff54">We did!</font>

1208
01:44:13.210 --> 01:44:13.770
<font color="#ffff54">You got it!</font>

1209
01:44:16.030 --> 01:44:17.230
<font color="#ffff54">Move it!</font>

1210
01:44:24.540 --> 01:44:25.860
<font color="#ffff54">Keep us straight!</font>

1211
01:44:33.510 --> 01:44:34.930
<font color="#ffff54">Keep us straight!</font>

1212
01:45:01.500 --> 01:45:02.380
<font color="#ffff54">You knew!</font>

1213
01:45:03.220 --> 01:45:04.560
<font color="#ffff54">And you didn't tell us!</font>

1214
01:45:04.900 --> 01:45:07.500
<font color="#ffff54">If I told you. you wouldn't have chosen this way.</font>

1215
01:45:07.700 --> 01:45:10.120
<font color="#ffff54">And those men would still be alive!</font>

1216
01:45:10.360 --> 01:45:11.640
<font color="#ffff54">No! We'd all be dead.</font>

1217
01:45:12.200 --> 01:45:13.240
<font color="#ffff54">You had no right!</font>

1218
01:45:13.440 --> 01:45:14.520
<font color="#ffff54">I had every right.</font>

1219
01:45:14.980 --> 01:45:16.420
<font color="#ffff54">And every responsibility.</font>

1220
01:45:16.940 --> 01:45:18.980
<font color="#ffff54">The Whirlpool would have destroyed the ship</font>

1221
01:45:18.980 --> 01:45:19.800
<font color="#ffff54">and all of us!</font>

1222
01:45:20.060 --> 01:45:21.100
<font color="#ffff54">This way we live!</font>

1223
01:45:21.280 --> 01:45:22.380
<font color="#ffff54">Some of us live!</font>

1224
01:45:22.580 --> 01:45:23.040
<font color="#ffff54">Yes!</font>

1225
01:45:26.800 --> 01:45:28.680
<font color="#ffff54">What else did Tyresius tell you?</font>

1226
01:45:40.300 --> 01:45:41.620
<font color="#ffff54">I'm gonna put in there.</font>

1227
01:45:44.180 --> 01:45:45.880
<font color="#ffff54">We can't land there.</font>

1228
01:45:46.060 --> 01:45:47.500
<font color="#ffff54">That's the sun god's isle.</font>

1229
01:45:47.840 --> 01:45:48.720
<font color="#ffff54">We need repairs!</font>

1230
01:45:50.340 --> 01:45:51.880
<font color="#ffff54">These men are exhausted!</font>

1231
01:45:52.160 --> 01:45:53.600
<font color="#ffff54">I lost six shipmates!</font>

1232
01:45:54.140 --> 01:45:54.940
<font color="#ffff54">You're gonna put in.</font>

1233
01:45:55.080 --> 01:45:56.820
<font color="#ffff54">I'm gonna rest up on dry land.</font>

1234
01:45:56.820 --> 01:45:58.220
<font color="#ffff54">You're all gonna die!</font>

1235
01:46:00.980 --> 01:46:03.360
<font color="#ffff54">You asked me what Tyresius told me.</font>

1236
01:46:03.980 --> 01:46:05.720
<font color="#ffff54">He said you're all gonna die.</font>

1237
01:46:06.240 --> 01:46:09.920
<font color="#ffff54">If you slaughter the sun god's cattle.</font>

1238
01:46:10.080 --> 01:46:11.640
<font color="#ffff54">which graze on that island.</font>

1239
01:46:11.880 --> 01:46:12.660
<font color="#ffff54">you'll all die.</font>

1240
01:46:16.930 --> 01:46:17.870
<font color="#ffff54">That's fine.</font>

1241
01:46:18.810 --> 01:46:19.870
<font color="#ffff54">We'll put in.</font>

1242
01:46:20.650 --> 01:46:22.270
<font color="#ffff54">We'll cook our own provisions.</font>

1243
01:46:22.590 --> 01:46:23.390
<font color="#ffff54">We'll pick fruit.</font>

1244
01:46:23.530 --> 01:46:24.150
<font color="#ffff54">We'll get water.</font>

1245
01:46:24.150 --> 01:46:24.810
<font color="#ffff54">We'll put in.</font>

1246
01:46:24.810 --> 01:46:25.210
<font color="#ffff54">Nothing more.</font>

1247
01:46:26.710 --> 01:46:27.690
<font color="#ffff54">Swear to it.</font>

1248
01:46:28.410 --> 01:46:29.290
<font color="#ffff54">All of you.</font>

1249
01:46:43.510 --> 01:46:44.050
<font color="#ffff54">See?</font>

1250
01:46:45.330 --> 01:46:46.910
<font color="#ffff54">The wind took us right in.</font>

1251
01:46:47.990 --> 01:46:49.090
<font color="#ffff54">We'll rest up.</font>

1252
01:46:49.750 --> 01:46:50.870
<font color="#ffff54">do the repairs.</font>

1253
01:46:51.250 --> 01:46:52.950
<font color="#ffff54">and set out as soon as the wind changes.</font>

1254
01:46:54.110 --> 01:46:55.030
<font color="#ffff54">Grab that light.</font>

1255
01:47:06.180 --> 01:47:07.980
<font color="#ffff54">Did the crew keep their promise?</font>

1256
01:47:09.260 --> 01:47:09.820
<font color="#ffff54">Yes.</font>

1257
01:47:10.920 --> 01:47:12.180
<font color="#ffff54">For a long time.</font>

1258
01:47:13.900 --> 01:47:15.620
<font color="#ffff54">But the wind never changed.</font>

1259
01:47:15.900 --> 01:47:17.620
<font color="#ffff54">The steady onshore breeze</font>

1260
01:47:17.620 --> 01:47:19.540
<font color="#ffff54">that made it so easy for us to land</font>

1261
01:47:22.060 --> 01:47:23.860
<font color="#ffff54">made it impossible to leave.</font>

1262
01:47:27.990 --> 01:47:29.670
<font color="#ffff54">And our provisions ran out.</font>

1263
01:47:32.870 --> 01:47:33.390
<font color="#ffff54">Go!</font>

1264
01:48:36.420 --> 01:48:38.180
<font color="#ffff54">Did you think if you ate quietly.</font>

1265
01:48:38.360 --> 01:48:39.500
<font color="#ffff54">the sun god wouldn't notice?</font>

1266
01:48:39.940 --> 01:48:41.440
<font color="#ffff54">We thought you wouldn't notice.</font>

1267
01:48:42.400 --> 01:48:43.540
<font color="#ffff54">I'm not the problem.</font>

1268
01:48:43.900 --> 01:48:45.080
<font color="#ffff54">I wanted you to live.</font>

1269
01:48:51.200 --> 01:48:52.220
<font color="#ffff54">Tyresius told you.</font>

1270
01:48:52.720 --> 01:48:53.540
<font color="#ffff54">Cersei told you.</font>

1271
01:48:53.620 --> 01:48:54.480
<font color="#ffff54">The gods told you.</font>

1272
01:48:55.380 --> 01:48:57.720
<font color="#ffff54">You gods don't speak in ways we understand.</font>

1273
01:48:57.720 --> 01:48:59.440
<font color="#ffff54">Who doesn't understand pain?</font>

1274
01:49:00.500 --> 01:49:01.260
<font color="#ffff54">Or blood?</font>

1275
01:49:01.380 --> 01:49:01.740
<font color="#ffff54">Or death?</font>

1276
01:49:02.740 --> 01:49:04.020
<font color="#ffff54">When you watch your man die.</font>

1277
01:49:04.080 --> 01:49:04.660
<font color="#ffff54">do you see chance.</font>

1278
01:49:04.700 --> 01:49:05.620
<font color="#ffff54">or do you see consequence?</font>

1279
01:49:06.520 --> 01:49:07.600
<font color="#ffff54">I see consequence.</font>

1280
01:49:07.940 --> 01:49:08.840
<font color="#ffff54">I see my failure.</font>

1281
01:49:09.540 --> 01:49:11.220
<font color="#ffff54">What if their deaths aren't your failure.</font>

1282
01:49:11.340 --> 01:49:11.700
<font color="#ffff54">but theirs?</font>

1283
01:49:12.460 --> 01:49:13.240
<font color="#ffff54">I lead them.</font>

1284
01:49:14.960 --> 01:49:16.040
<font color="#ffff54">I led them here.</font>

1285
01:49:16.740 --> 01:49:17.600
<font color="#ffff54">And who led you?</font>

1286
01:49:19.140 --> 01:49:20.920
<font color="#ffff54">Why do you put yourself above the gods?</font>

1287
01:49:21.000 --> 01:49:22.380
<font color="#ffff54">Why do you claim responsibility?</font>

1288
01:49:23.640 --> 01:49:25.060
<font color="#ffff54">Why don't you want to go home?</font>

1289
01:49:25.380 --> 01:49:26.560
<font color="#ffff54">What do you expect?</font>

1290
01:49:28.400 --> 01:49:29.900
<font color="#ffff54">They ran out of food.</font>

1291
01:49:31.040 --> 01:49:32.100
<font color="#ffff54">Have some pity.</font>

1292
01:49:32.280 --> 01:49:35.100
<font color="#ffff54">My pity is what put us on this damn island.</font>

1293
01:49:35.280 --> 01:49:36.520
<font color="#ffff54">I told you what would happen.</font>

1294
01:49:36.780 --> 01:49:37.420
<font color="#ffff54">Yes. you did.</font>

1295
01:49:38.200 --> 01:49:41.120
<font color="#ffff54">And we decided we would rather drown than starve.</font>

1296
01:49:47.490 --> 01:49:48.970
<font color="#ffff54">Well. now's our chance.</font>

1297
01:49:49.470 --> 01:49:50.510
<font color="#ffff54">The wind is dropped!</font>

1298
01:49:50.810 --> 01:49:51.590
<font color="#ffff54">The wind is dropped!</font>

1299
01:49:55.370 --> 01:49:57.210
<font color="#ffff54">The calm was just long enough</font>

1300
01:49:57.210 --> 01:49:59.150
<font color="#ffff54">to lure us out onto Poseidon's ocean.</font>

1301
01:50:00.430 --> 01:50:01.770
<font color="#ffff54">Under Zeus' sky.</font>

1302
01:51:53.400 --> 01:51:56.820
<font color="#ffff54">The last thing I remember was the harsh hand of Zeus.</font>

1303
01:52:41.770 --> 01:52:43.430
<font color="#ffff54">I don't know what happened to my men.</font>

1304
01:52:43.670 --> 01:52:44.410
<font color="#ffff54">Yes. you do.</font>

1305
01:52:46.770 --> 01:52:48.330
<font color="#ffff54">Exactly what you told them would happen.</font>

1306
01:52:48.330 --> 01:52:50.970
<font color="#ffff54">I washed up on your shore alone.</font>

1307
01:52:51.230 --> 01:52:53.070
<font color="#ffff54">You washed up on my shore</font>

1308
01:52:53.070 --> 01:52:54.690
<font color="#ffff54">with some of your boat</font>

1309
01:52:54.690 --> 01:52:55.770
<font color="#ffff54">and none of your crew.</font>

1310
01:52:57.890 --> 01:52:59.910
<font color="#ffff54">Half dead. unconscious.</font>

1311
01:53:22.650 --> 01:53:26.490
<font color="#ffff54">I watched you lost for days</font>

1312
01:53:27.170 --> 01:53:28.350
<font color="#ffff54">into weeks.</font>

1313
01:53:29.110 --> 01:53:31.730
<font color="#ffff54">I knew the Lotus would ease your awakening</font>

1314
01:53:33.350 --> 01:53:36.150
<font color="#ffff54">so that your pain was more of the body than the mind.</font>

1315
01:53:38.730 --> 01:53:39.850
<font color="#ffff54">And it did.</font>

1316
01:53:42.410 --> 01:53:44.270
<font color="#ffff54">You liked it so much.</font>

1317
01:53:45.390 --> 01:53:47.390
<font color="#ffff54">You ate it so willingly.</font>

1318
01:53:51.150 --> 01:53:52.750
<font color="#ffff54">And as I cared for you.</font>

1319
01:53:53.310 --> 01:53:54.050
<font color="#ffff54">Thank you.</font>

1320
01:53:54.770 --> 01:53:55.850
<font color="#ffff54">I came to love you.</font>

1321
01:54:01.440 --> 01:54:02.940
<font color="#ffff54">How long have I been here?</font>

1322
01:54:05.240 --> 01:54:08.080
<font color="#ffff54">I kept telling myself to stop giving it to you.</font>

1323
01:54:08.240 --> 01:54:09.960
<font color="#ffff54">That you were strong enough to remember.</font>

1324
01:54:09.960 --> 01:54:11.180
<font color="#ffff54">How long. Calypso?</font>

1325
01:54:11.280 --> 01:54:12.400
<font color="#ffff54">You were so happy.</font>

1326
01:54:12.580 --> 01:54:13.320
<font color="#ffff54">You were happy.</font>

1327
01:54:13.440 --> 01:54:15.020
<font color="#ffff54">We were so happy.</font>

1328
01:54:15.220 --> 01:54:16.020
<font color="#ffff54">For years.</font>

1329
01:54:16.540 --> 01:54:16.960
<font color="#ffff54">Years?</font>

1330
01:54:23.970 --> 01:54:25.030
<font color="#ffff54">Seven years.</font>

1331
01:54:25.910 --> 01:54:27.930
<font color="#ffff54">You fed me lotus flower</font>

1332
01:54:27.930 --> 01:54:29.710
<font color="#ffff54">and held me captive.</font>

1333
01:54:30.010 --> 01:54:31.370
<font color="#ffff54">I saved your life.</font>

1334
01:54:31.970 --> 01:54:33.610
<font color="#ffff54">I rebuilt your body.</font>

1335
01:54:33.750 --> 01:54:35.030
<font color="#ffff54">I just couldn't bring myself</font>

1336
01:54:35.030 --> 01:54:36.310
<font color="#ffff54">to rebuild your mind.</font>

1337
01:54:37.570 --> 01:54:39.030
<font color="#ffff54">You have been happy.</font>

1338
01:54:39.810 --> 01:54:40.890
<font color="#ffff54">Your heart</font>

1339
01:54:40.890 --> 01:54:43.090
<font color="#ffff54">was just always somewhere else.</font>

1340
01:54:44.310 --> 01:54:45.410
<font color="#ffff54">And your mind</font>

1341
01:54:45.410 --> 01:54:46.890
<font color="#ffff54">was bound to follow</font>

1342
01:54:46.890 --> 01:54:47.470
<font color="#ffff54">eventually.</font>

1343
01:54:48.790 --> 01:54:49.790
<font color="#ffff54">How could you?</font>

1344
01:54:50.250 --> 01:54:51.610
<font color="#ffff54">The lotus clouds</font>

1345
01:54:51.610 --> 01:54:52.310
<font color="#ffff54">the mind</font>

1346
01:54:52.310 --> 01:54:53.670
<font color="#ffff54">and saps the well</font>

1347
01:54:53.670 --> 01:54:54.690
<font color="#ffff54">but it doesn't change</font>

1348
01:54:54.690 --> 01:54:55.570
<font color="#ffff54">who you are.</font>

1349
01:54:56.090 --> 01:54:57.250
<font color="#ffff54">You weren't ready</font>

1350
01:54:57.250 --> 01:54:58.030
<font color="#ffff54">to go home</font>

1351
01:54:58.030 --> 01:54:59.070
<font color="#ffff54">for whatever reason.</font>

1352
01:54:59.490 --> 01:55:00.550
<font color="#ffff54">I am now.</font>

1353
01:55:02.030 --> 01:55:03.290
<font color="#ffff54">As I always knew</font>

1354
01:55:03.290 --> 01:55:03.890
<font color="#ffff54">you would be.</font>

1355
01:55:04.870 --> 01:55:05.310
<font color="#ffff54">How?</font>

1356
01:55:05.750 --> 01:55:07.270
<font color="#ffff54">You were clutching something</font>

1357
01:55:07.270 --> 01:55:08.370
<font color="#ffff54">when I found you.</font>

1358
01:55:08.830 --> 01:55:09.810
<font color="#ffff54">Your hand wouldn't open</font>

1359
01:55:09.810 --> 01:55:10.370
<font color="#ffff54">for weeks.</font>

1360
01:55:11.130 --> 01:55:12.410
<font color="#ffff54">You'd call out.</font>

1361
01:55:13.150 --> 01:55:14.450
<font color="#ffff54">Mostly to Athena</font>

1362
01:55:14.450 --> 01:55:16.030
<font color="#ffff54">but sometimes</font>

1363
01:55:16.030 --> 01:55:16.750
<font color="#ffff54">you would say</font>

1364
01:55:16.750 --> 01:55:17.450
<font color="#ffff54">another name.</font>

1365
01:55:36.730 --> 01:55:38.230
<font color="#ffff54">Help me go home.</font>

1366
01:55:38.830 --> 01:55:39.930
<font color="#ffff54">I am.</font>

1367
01:55:41.170 --> 01:55:42.150
<font color="#ffff54">You're a man</font>

1368
01:55:42.150 --> 01:55:43.030
<font color="#ffff54">who needs to control</font>

1369
01:55:43.030 --> 01:55:43.630
<font color="#ffff54">his fate</font>

1370
01:55:45.010 --> 01:55:46.410
<font color="#ffff54">but you cannot control</font>

1371
01:55:46.410 --> 01:55:46.830
<font color="#ffff54">this.</font>

1372
01:55:50.050 --> 01:55:51.370
<font color="#ffff54">You must give yourself</font>

1373
01:55:51.370 --> 01:55:52.150
<font color="#ffff54">to the storm</font>

1374
01:55:52.150 --> 01:55:53.750
<font color="#ffff54">give yourself</font>

1375
01:55:53.750 --> 01:55:54.650
<font color="#ffff54">to Poseidon</font>

1376
01:55:56.010 --> 01:55:57.450
<font color="#ffff54">and take your punishment.</font>

1377
01:56:00.330 --> 01:56:01.510
<font color="#ffff54">Zeus won't let him</font>

1378
01:56:01.510 --> 01:56:01.990
<font color="#ffff54">kill you.</font>

1379
01:56:05.610 --> 01:56:06.930
<font color="#ffff54">Give up the fight</font>

1380
01:56:06.930 --> 01:56:08.050
<font color="#ffff54">give up control</font>

1381
01:56:08.050 --> 01:56:08.870
<font color="#ffff54">and live</font>

1382
01:56:11.790 --> 01:56:12.670
<font color="#ffff54">and to leave</font>

1383
01:56:12.670 --> 01:56:13.190
<font color="#ffff54">a fate</font>

1384
01:56:13.190 --> 01:56:14.690
<font color="#ffff54">you've never yet</font>

1385
01:56:14.690 --> 01:56:15.870
<font color="#ffff54">made Odysseus.</font>

1386
01:57:08.150 --> 01:57:08.730
<font color="#ffff54">Odysseus.</font>

1387
01:57:16.960 --> 01:57:17.980
<font color="#ffff54">Where am I?</font>

1388
01:57:20.120 --> 01:57:21.220
<font color="#ffff54">Don't you recognize</font>

1389
01:57:21.220 --> 01:57:21.920
<font color="#ffff54">your own home?</font>

1390
01:58:01.220 --> 01:58:02.540
<font color="#ffff54">Zeus welcomes you</font>

1391
01:58:02.540 --> 01:58:02.940
<font color="#ffff54">strangers.</font>

1392
01:58:04.120 --> 01:58:05.280
<font color="#ffff54">How many are you?</font>

1393
01:58:06.040 --> 01:58:06.840
<font color="#ffff54">Half a dozen.</font>

1394
01:58:07.760 --> 01:58:08.500
<font color="#ffff54">Need of a meal?</font>

1395
01:58:08.980 --> 01:58:09.900
<font color="#ffff54">And supplies</font>

1396
01:58:09.900 --> 01:58:11.480
<font color="#ffff54">for the road.</font>

1397
01:58:12.080 --> 01:58:13.040
<font color="#ffff54">Where are you headed?</font>

1398
01:58:13.380 --> 01:58:14.440
<font color="#ffff54">We need pigs.</font>

1399
01:58:14.840 --> 01:58:15.840
<font color="#ffff54">We're going all the way</font>

1400
01:58:15.840 --> 01:58:16.500
<font color="#ffff54">to Pylos.</font>

1401
01:58:16.900 --> 01:58:17.980
<font color="#ffff54">Are you pilgrims?</font>

1402
01:58:18.940 --> 01:58:20.600
<font color="#ffff54">Do we look like pilgrims?</font>

1403
01:58:20.600 --> 01:58:21.960
<font color="#ffff54">I don't see well.</font>

1404
01:58:23.200 --> 01:58:24.120
<font color="#ffff54">Zeus demands</font>

1405
01:58:24.120 --> 01:58:25.080
<font color="#ffff54">I offer you a meal</font>

1406
01:58:25.080 --> 01:58:25.860
<font color="#ffff54">but these pigs</font>

1407
01:58:25.860 --> 01:58:26.940
<font color="#ffff54">aren't mine to sell.</font>

1408
01:58:27.220 --> 01:58:27.940
<font color="#ffff54">Oh don't worry.</font>

1409
01:58:28.720 --> 01:58:29.640
<font color="#ffff54">We're not paying.</font>

1410
01:58:33.260 --> 01:58:34.460
<font color="#ffff54">Give my greetings</font>

1411
01:58:34.460 --> 01:58:35.240
<font color="#ffff54">to your mother.</font>

1412
01:58:38.540 --> 01:58:39.780
<font color="#ffff54">Tell her I'm sorry.</font>

1413
01:58:40.160 --> 01:58:41.460
<font color="#ffff54">I'm sorry for Troy.</font>

1414
01:58:50.460 --> 01:58:51.440
<font color="#ffff54">I'm sorry I had</font>

1415
01:58:51.440 --> 01:58:52.560
<font color="#ffff54">no news of your father.</font>

1416
01:58:53.000 --> 01:58:54.000
<font color="#ffff54">No. you had news.</font>

1417
01:58:54.440 --> 01:58:55.600
<font color="#ffff54">Not of where he is</font>

1418
01:58:55.600 --> 01:58:56.320
<font color="#ffff54">but who he is.</font>

1419
01:58:57.820 --> 01:58:58.980
<font color="#ffff54">And now more than ever</font>

1420
01:58:58.980 --> 01:58:59.660
<font color="#ffff54">I hope to one day</font>

1421
01:58:59.660 --> 01:59:00.080
<font color="#ffff54">meet him.</font>

1422
01:59:05.130 --> 01:59:06.130
<font color="#ffff54">Where are your</font>

1423
01:59:06.130 --> 01:59:07.350
<font color="#ffff54">watchdogs old man?</font>

1424
01:59:11.800 --> 01:59:13.580
<font color="#ffff54">I'm burning their bodies.</font>

1425
01:59:18.170 --> 01:59:19.650
<font color="#ffff54">Can Zeus offer you</font>

1426
01:59:19.650 --> 01:59:20.870
<font color="#ffff54">food and drake stranger?</font>

1427
01:59:21.810 --> 01:59:22.870
<font color="#ffff54">Were you attacked?</font>

1428
01:59:23.630 --> 01:59:24.710
<font color="#ffff54">The dog saved</font>

1429
01:59:24.710 --> 01:59:25.430
<font color="#ffff54">your farm heads.</font>

1430
01:59:25.950 --> 01:59:26.830
<font color="#ffff54">Oh. he burned</font>

1431
01:59:26.830 --> 01:59:27.810
<font color="#ffff54">his brothers first.</font>

1432
01:59:30.690 --> 01:59:32.270
<font color="#ffff54">What happened to Ithaca?</font>

1433
01:59:33.190 --> 01:59:33.890
<font color="#ffff54">Darkness.</font>

1434
01:59:34.350 --> 01:59:35.350
<font color="#ffff54">Zeus' law</font>

1435
01:59:35.350 --> 01:59:36.670
<font color="#ffff54">smashed to pieces.</font>

1436
01:59:36.670 --> 01:59:38.430
<font color="#ffff54">a kingdom</font>

1437
01:59:38.430 --> 01:59:39.350
<font color="#ffff54">without a king</font>

1438
01:59:39.350 --> 01:59:40.390
<font color="#ffff54">since my master</font>

1439
01:59:40.390 --> 01:59:40.870
<font color="#ffff54">died.</font>

1440
01:59:41.130 --> 01:59:41.950
<font color="#ffff54">Your master?</font>

1441
01:59:43.290 --> 01:59:44.090
<font color="#ffff54">Odysseus.</font>

1442
01:59:44.790 --> 01:59:46.470
<font color="#ffff54">Hero of the Trojan War.</font>

1443
01:59:48.550 --> 01:59:50.370
<font color="#ffff54">But Odysseus is alive.</font>

1444
01:59:50.670 --> 01:59:53.690
<font color="#ffff54">No more!</font>

1445
01:59:53.950 --> 01:59:54.430
<font color="#ffff54">No more!</font>

1446
01:59:54.430 --> 01:59:55.910
<font color="#ffff54">No more!</font>

1447
01:59:56.290 --> 01:59:56.610
<font color="#ffff54">No more!</font>

1448
01:59:56.610 --> 01:59:57.530
<font color="#ffff54">No more!</font>

1449
01:59:57.850 --> 01:59:58.170
<font color="#ffff54">No more!</font>

1450
01:59:59.350 --> 01:59:59.910
<font color="#ffff54">Telemachus.</font>

1451
02:00:00.450 --> 02:00:01.010
<font color="#ffff54">Telemachus.</font>

1452
02:00:02.410 --> 02:00:02.970
<font color="#ffff54">Telemachus.</font>

1453
02:00:03.150 --> 02:00:03.930
<font color="#ffff54">He's in danger.</font>

1454
02:00:04.310 --> 02:00:05.430
<font color="#ffff54">He's in danger</font>

1455
02:00:05.430 --> 02:00:06.450
<font color="#ffff54">and I can't help him.</font>

1456
02:00:06.870 --> 02:00:07.830
<font color="#ffff54">There must be others</font>

1457
02:00:07.830 --> 02:00:08.330
<font color="#ffff54">in this</font>

1458
02:00:08.330 --> 02:00:08.930
<font color="#ffff54">because it would</font>

1459
02:00:08.930 --> 02:00:10.350
<font color="#ffff54">help Odysseus' son.</font>

1460
02:00:10.550 --> 02:00:11.170
<font color="#ffff54">The palace is</font>

1461
02:00:11.170 --> 02:00:12.510
<font color="#ffff54">controlled by suitors.</font>

1462
02:00:13.150 --> 02:00:14.630
<font color="#ffff54">No one still loyal</font>

1463
02:00:14.630 --> 02:00:15.670
<font color="#ffff54">to Odysseus.</font>

1464
02:00:16.810 --> 02:00:18.010
<font color="#ffff54">What about the queen?</font>

1465
02:00:19.010 --> 02:00:26.790
<font color="#ffff54">Beautiful. wise Penelope. held hostage by the worst men. soon to be forced into marriage.</font>

1466
02:00:26.790 --> 02:00:28.990
<font color="#ffff54">What could she do without even her son?</font>

1467
02:00:29.430 --> 02:00:30.270
<font color="#ffff54">Here. drink.</font>

1468
02:00:35.260 --> 02:00:37.060
<font color="#ffff54">What's the danger to Telemachus?</font>

1469
02:00:37.800 --> 02:00:39.980
<font color="#ffff54">He's on his way back from Sparta.</font>

1470
02:00:41.060 --> 02:00:45.860
<font color="#ffff54">The suitors sent bandits to Pylos to ambush him at the temple.</font>

1471
02:00:46.680 --> 02:00:48.080
<font color="#ffff54">Give me food for the road.</font>

1472
02:00:49.600 --> 02:00:51.540
<font color="#ffff54">You'll never catch up with the bandits.</font>

1473
02:00:52.000 --> 02:00:55.140
<font color="#ffff54">If I can get to Pylos before Telemachus arrives. I can warn him.</font>

1474
02:00:55.780 --> 02:00:56.960
<font color="#ffff54">Why are you helping?</font>

1475
02:00:57.820 --> 02:00:59.700
<font color="#ffff54">If I tell you. don't be angry.</font>

1476
02:01:00.260 --> 02:01:02.300
<font color="#ffff54">I served with Odysseus at Troy.</font>

1477
02:01:02.540 --> 02:01:03.060
<font color="#ffff54">Really?</font>

1478
02:01:04.480 --> 02:01:06.180
<font color="#ffff54">He was a harsh taskmaster.</font>

1479
02:01:06.380 --> 02:01:07.320
<font color="#ffff54">Oh. but fair.</font>

1480
02:01:08.920 --> 02:01:10.880
<font color="#ffff54">Fair and worthy of following.</font>

1481
02:01:12.240 --> 02:01:13.240
<font color="#ffff54">You loved him.</font>

1482
02:01:14.180 --> 02:01:15.280
<font color="#ffff54">Like a son.</font>

1483
02:01:16.760 --> 02:01:18.580
<font color="#ffff54">Well. he's not dead.</font>

1484
02:01:19.120 --> 02:01:20.800
<font color="#ffff54">Is he coming home?</font>

1485
02:01:21.880 --> 02:01:22.460
<font color="#ffff54">Soon.</font>

1486
02:01:23.260 --> 02:01:24.580
<font color="#ffff54">Bringing vengeance.</font>

1487
02:01:26.940 --> 02:01:28.280
<font color="#ffff54">Bringing it all.</font>

1488
02:01:37.660 --> 02:01:38.600
<font color="#ffff54">I'll talk.</font>

1489
02:01:38.840 --> 02:01:40.700
<font color="#ffff54">We don't want people realizing where you are.</font>

1490
02:01:40.920 --> 02:01:42.540
<font color="#ffff54">Maybe we shouldn't have brought a guard.</font>

1491
02:01:43.000 --> 02:01:45.240
<font color="#ffff54">We'll be glad we did if we have trouble on the road.</font>

1492
02:02:05.460 --> 02:02:06.400
<font color="#ffff54">Find that beggar.</font>

1493
02:02:22.540 --> 02:02:23.980
<font color="#ffff54">Your men must wait out here.</font>

1494
02:02:24.220 --> 02:02:25.080
<font color="#ffff54">The weapons. too.</font>

1495
02:02:42.590 --> 02:02:43.830
<font color="#ffff54">Zeus welcomes you strangers.</font>

1496
02:02:44.450 --> 02:02:45.590
<font color="#ffff54">Have you traveled far?</font>

1497
02:02:46.070 --> 02:02:47.150
<font color="#ffff54">Not that far.</font>

1498
02:02:48.470 --> 02:02:50.350
<font color="#ffff54">You're here to rest for the night.</font>

1499
02:02:52.430 --> 02:02:54.550
<font color="#ffff54">We're here to make sacrifice to Athena.</font>

1500
02:02:56.710 --> 02:02:59.750
<font color="#ffff54">And whatever hospitality you can offer might be considered.</font>

1501
02:03:00.210 --> 02:03:00.790
<font color="#ffff54">Of course.</font>

1502
02:03:01.030 --> 02:03:02.530
<font color="#ffff54">Get that beggar out of here.</font>

1503
02:03:02.610 --> 02:03:03.830
<font color="#ffff54">He has a message for me.</font>

1504
02:03:04.830 --> 02:03:06.070
<font color="#ffff54">He may have sent you.</font>

1505
02:03:07.370 --> 02:03:08.130
<font color="#ffff54">Yes. sir.</font>

1506
02:03:14.170 --> 02:03:15.430
<font color="#ffff54">Well. what's the message?</font>

1507
02:03:16.910 --> 02:03:17.890
<font color="#ffff54">It's private.</font>

1508
02:03:17.890 --> 02:03:19.390
<font color="#ffff54">These men are pretty.</font>

1509
02:03:21.110 --> 02:03:22.250
<font color="#ffff54">These men are pretty.</font>

1510
02:03:39.790 --> 02:03:41.870
<font color="#ffff54">This is your moment to leave. old man.</font>

1511
02:03:42.770 --> 02:03:43.430
<font color="#ffff54">Go. stranger.</font>

1512
02:03:46.170 --> 02:03:48.430
<font color="#ffff54">I already spared one old man this week.</font>

1513
02:03:48.850 --> 02:03:50.030
<font color="#ffff54">But he was blind.</font>

1514
02:03:50.030 --> 02:03:52.110
<font color="#ffff54">I won't spare them.</font>

1515
02:03:52.570 --> 02:03:54.710
<font color="#ffff54">I won't spare them.</font>

1516
02:04:30.820 --> 02:04:32.180
<font color="#ffff54">Not bad for a beggar.</font>

1517
02:04:32.940 --> 02:04:34.260
<font color="#ffff54">No one's born a beggar.</font>

1518
02:04:34.980 --> 02:04:37.880
<font color="#ffff54">We'll take this priest's robes. put them over your armor.</font>

1519
02:04:40.180 --> 02:04:41.360
<font color="#ffff54">Help me with his body.</font>

1520
02:04:41.640 --> 02:04:42.460
<font color="#ffff54">We have to leave him.</font>

1521
02:04:43.080 --> 02:04:43.480
<font color="#ffff54">No.</font>

1522
02:04:43.760 --> 02:04:44.800
<font color="#ffff54">We have to slip out.</font>

1523
02:04:45.580 --> 02:04:47.040
<font color="#ffff54">That's not how you honor the dead.</font>

1524
02:04:47.200 --> 02:04:48.440
<font color="#ffff54">That is how you stay alive.</font>

1525
02:04:48.640 --> 02:04:49.520
<font color="#ffff54">He was my teacher.</font>

1526
02:04:50.880 --> 02:04:52.440
<font color="#ffff54">He might have been Athena in disguise.</font>

1527
02:04:52.440 --> 02:04:53.740
<font color="#ffff54">His name was Mentor.</font>

1528
02:04:54.380 --> 02:04:57.280
<font color="#ffff54">And when you are safe. we'll travel to the unknown west.</font>

1529
02:04:57.780 --> 02:04:58.980
<font color="#ffff54">And we will honor him.</font>

1530
02:04:59.460 --> 02:05:01.020
<font color="#ffff54">These men were sent by the suitors.</font>

1531
02:05:01.480 --> 02:05:03.640
<font color="#ffff54">There will be more of them we need to get on the road.</font>

1532
02:05:03.940 --> 02:05:04.540
<font color="#ffff54">By night?</font>

1533
02:05:04.840 --> 02:05:06.000
<font color="#ffff54">Safer than staying here.</font>

1534
02:05:06.700 --> 02:05:08.700
<font color="#ffff54">Mentor's at the heart of Athena's oldest temple.</font>

1535
02:05:09.280 --> 02:05:11.480
<font color="#ffff54">For now. we'll honor him in flame.</font>

1536
02:05:50.350 --> 02:05:52.210
<font color="#ffff54">So how does a beggar come to know Mentor?</font>

1537
02:05:52.390 --> 02:05:53.290
<font color="#ffff54">I told you.</font>

1538
02:05:53.470 --> 02:05:54.850
<font color="#ffff54">I wasn't always a beggar.</font>

1539
02:05:55.350 --> 02:05:56.750
<font color="#ffff54">You have wise eyes.</font>

1540
02:05:57.850 --> 02:05:58.410
<font color="#ffff54">Athena's eyes.</font>

1541
02:05:58.850 --> 02:05:59.750
<font color="#ffff54">You're gods and men.</font>

1542
02:05:59.990 --> 02:06:01.010
<font color="#ffff54">You'll just be disappointed.</font>

1543
02:06:01.750 --> 02:06:03.410
<font color="#ffff54">Well. then tell me who you are.</font>

1544
02:06:05.070 --> 02:06:06.370
<font color="#ffff54">My name is Sinon.</font>

1545
02:06:07.070 --> 02:06:09.950
<font color="#ffff54">I'm an old soldier who fought under your father at Troy.</font>

1546
02:06:11.350 --> 02:06:12.350
<font color="#ffff54">You knew my father?</font>

1547
02:06:12.830 --> 02:06:15.930
<font color="#ffff54">I've been taking orders from him for longer than I care to remember.</font>

1548
02:06:16.930 --> 02:06:18.010
<font color="#ffff54">Wait. he's alive?</font>

1549
02:06:19.250 --> 02:06:20.090
<font color="#ffff54">He's alive.</font>

1550
02:06:21.870 --> 02:06:23.050
<font color="#ffff54">Well. where is he?</font>

1551
02:06:23.570 --> 02:06:23.930
<font color="#ffff54">Well. where is he?</font>

1552
02:06:23.930 --> 02:06:24.650
<font color="#ffff54">He's close by.</font>

1553
02:06:25.510 --> 02:06:27.590
<font color="#ffff54">He sent me ahead to assess the situation.</font>

1554
02:06:29.190 --> 02:06:30.930
<font color="#ffff54">Well. mother's not gonna believe it.</font>

1555
02:06:31.170 --> 02:06:32.290
<font color="#ffff54">No. you can't tell her.</font>

1556
02:06:33.530 --> 02:06:34.330
<font color="#ffff54">What. nothing?</font>

1557
02:06:35.770 --> 02:06:36.490
<font color="#ffff54">Tell her.</font>

1558
02:06:37.970 --> 02:06:38.590
<font color="#ffff54">Tell her.</font>

1559
02:06:38.650 --> 02:06:40.330
<font color="#ffff54">Tell her he decided it's time she remarried.</font>

1560
02:06:42.150 --> 02:06:43.790
<font color="#ffff54">He doesn't need to test my mother.</font>

1561
02:06:43.910 --> 02:06:44.650
<font color="#ffff54">How can he doubt her?</font>

1562
02:06:44.950 --> 02:06:45.690
<font color="#ffff54">He doesn't.</font>

1563
02:06:46.290 --> 02:06:48.630
<font color="#ffff54">But she has every reason to have forgotten him.</font>

1564
02:06:50.390 --> 02:06:52.050
<font color="#ffff54">Are there any loyal servants?</font>

1565
02:06:53.270 --> 02:06:53.830
<font color="#ffff54">Some?</font>

1566
02:06:55.230 --> 02:06:56.970
<font color="#ffff54">Well. he just shows himself all.</font>

1567
02:06:58.430 --> 02:07:00.630
<font color="#ffff54">We need to gather the suitors at the palace.</font>

1568
02:07:01.570 --> 02:07:02.830
<font color="#ffff54">That's never a problem.</font>

1569
02:07:03.730 --> 02:07:05.050
<font color="#ffff54">You have gifts for Menelaus?</font>

1570
02:07:05.050 --> 02:07:06.510
<font color="#ffff54">Yeah. on my ship.</font>

1571
02:07:07.390 --> 02:07:07.670
<font color="#ffff54">Good.</font>

1572
02:07:08.570 --> 02:07:09.790
<font color="#ffff54">Come back as a prince.</font>

1573
02:07:10.510 --> 02:07:11.170
<font color="#ffff54">Call a banquet.</font>

1574
02:07:11.990 --> 02:07:12.850
<font color="#ffff54">I'll be there.</font>

1575
02:07:13.970 --> 02:07:15.390
<font color="#ffff54">What will you do at the banquet?</font>

1576
02:07:16.350 --> 02:07:16.830
<font color="#ffff54">Beg.</font>

1577
02:07:17.630 --> 02:07:19.710
<font color="#ffff54">The clearest view of a man is from below.</font>

1578
02:07:21.730 --> 02:07:23.130
<font color="#ffff54">How many suitors are there?</font>

1579
02:07:24.170 --> 02:07:24.650
<font color="#ffff54">Dozens.</font>

1580
02:07:25.490 --> 02:07:27.430
<font color="#ffff54">If all of his men are like you. then...</font>

1581
02:07:27.430 --> 02:07:28.550
<font color="#ffff54">He doesn't have any men.</font>

1582
02:07:29.510 --> 02:07:30.510
<font color="#ffff54">But it's just you?</font>

1583
02:07:32.010 --> 02:07:32.750
<font color="#ffff54">And you.</font>

1584
02:07:39.090 --> 02:07:40.290
<font color="#ffff54">Telemachus is back.</font>

1585
02:07:40.490 --> 02:07:40.730
<font color="#ffff54">What?</font>

1586
02:07:40.910 --> 02:07:41.870
<font color="#ffff54">Telemachus is back.</font>

1587
02:07:42.470 --> 02:07:43.650
<font color="#ffff54">Who's saying this?</font>

1588
02:07:44.050 --> 02:07:45.450
<font color="#ffff54">Everyone's thinking of...</font>

1589
02:07:45.450 --> 02:07:46.570
<font color="#ffff54">Where's Telemachus?</font>

1590
02:07:47.110 --> 02:07:48.010
<font color="#ffff54">My queen!</font>

1591
02:07:48.570 --> 02:07:49.950
<font color="#ffff54">Surely your place is up there.</font>

1592
02:07:57.930 --> 02:07:58.950
<font color="#ffff54">Is it true?</font>

1593
02:08:02.030 --> 02:08:02.990
<font color="#ffff54">You're home?</font>

1594
02:08:04.170 --> 02:08:04.910
<font color="#ffff54">I'm back.</font>

1595
02:08:05.910 --> 02:08:07.250
<font color="#ffff54">I thought tonight we could celebrate.</font>

1596
02:08:08.070 --> 02:08:11.210
<font color="#ffff54">If we have anything left to celebrate with.</font>

1597
02:08:12.830 --> 02:08:13.530
<font color="#ffff54">Don't worry.</font>

1598
02:08:14.250 --> 02:08:17.210
<font color="#ffff54">My brave suitors will shower us with gifts to honor your return.</font>

1599
02:08:17.610 --> 02:08:19.070
<font color="#ffff54">So glad to see your safe return.</font>

1600
02:08:30.050 --> 02:08:31.370
<font color="#ffff54">Glad to see you on your feet.</font>

1601
02:08:31.990 --> 02:08:33.970
<font color="#ffff54">It's about time we took you back to the palace.</font>

1602
02:08:37.700 --> 02:08:38.980
<font color="#ffff54">What did you hear about your father?</font>

1603
02:08:41.360 --> 02:08:41.760
<font color="#ffff54">Nothing.</font>

1604
02:08:43.220 --> 02:08:46.420
<font color="#ffff54">Stories from the war. but no one knew what happened to him after he left Troy.</font>

1605
02:08:47.000 --> 02:08:48.000
<font color="#ffff54">I'm sorry mom.</font>

1606
02:08:49.440 --> 02:08:52.600
<font color="#ffff54">Everyone in Sparta is talking about a coming catastrophe.</font>

1607
02:08:53.640 --> 02:08:57.660
<font color="#ffff54">An age of darkness brought on by people from the sea violating Zeus' law.</font>

1608
02:08:57.900 --> 02:08:58.980
<font color="#ffff54">Then stories are true.</font>

1609
02:08:59.280 --> 02:09:00.920
<font color="#ffff54">Our civilization is collapsing.</font>

1610
02:09:01.620 --> 02:09:04.280
<font color="#ffff54">Menelaus is concerned that we can't raise an army with an empty throne.</font>

1611
02:09:04.740 --> 02:09:06.080
<font color="#ffff54">So we came up with a plan.</font>

1612
02:09:07.780 --> 02:09:08.500
<font color="#ffff54">What plan?</font>

1613
02:09:10.940 --> 02:09:12.740
<font color="#ffff54">The one way to get the suitors to leave.</font>

1614
02:09:15.300 --> 02:09:16.620
<font color="#ffff54">It's time for you to choose.</font>

1615
02:09:20.660 --> 02:09:21.860
<font color="#ffff54">You want me to remarry?</font>

1616
02:09:22.400 --> 02:09:25.200
<font color="#ffff54">If you remarry. the other suitors will leave.</font>

1617
02:09:25.360 --> 02:09:27.060
<font color="#ffff54">And then I'm only dealing with one of them.</font>

1618
02:09:27.380 --> 02:09:28.440
<font color="#ffff54">I'm almost of age.</font>

1619
02:09:28.540 --> 02:09:31.380
<font color="#ffff54">I'll tell the elders that I learned of Odysseus' death in Sparta.</font>

1620
02:09:32.640 --> 02:09:35.440
<font color="#ffff54">Menelaus will back me up and they'll let me assume the throne.</font>

1621
02:09:35.440 --> 02:09:39.020
<font color="#ffff54">So you deny your father and I leave my home and go live with one of these snakes.</font>

1622
02:09:39.220 --> 02:09:39.700
<font color="#ffff54">That's your plan.</font>

1623
02:09:40.240 --> 02:09:41.240
<font color="#ffff54">Would you have a better one?</font>

1624
02:09:44.300 --> 02:09:47.360
<font color="#ffff54">Lock the door. set afire. and burn the bastards.</font>

1625
02:09:48.800 --> 02:09:52.280
<font color="#ffff54">Do you think if I remarry. life goes back to the way it was?</font>

1626
02:09:53.380 --> 02:09:54.580
<font color="#ffff54">That world is gone.</font>

1627
02:09:55.320 --> 02:09:58.280
<font color="#ffff54">And in this one. they're not giving up power to you.</font>

1628
02:09:59.040 --> 02:09:59.840
<font color="#ffff54">Or Odysseus.</font>

1629
02:09:59.840 --> 02:10:01.860
<font color="#ffff54">If he returned. he'd have to kill them.</font>

1630
02:10:02.280 --> 02:10:03.200
<font color="#ffff54">Like you will.</font>

1631
02:10:04.100 --> 02:10:07.340
<font color="#ffff54">If I kill them. their families will demand revenge.</font>

1632
02:10:07.500 --> 02:10:08.400
<font color="#ffff54">I'd be exiled.</font>

1633
02:10:09.380 --> 02:10:11.500
<font color="#ffff54">And without me. the throne will be lost.</font>

1634
02:10:11.540 --> 02:10:13.040
<font color="#ffff54">Because only a man can sit on it.</font>

1635
02:10:15.120 --> 02:10:16.020
<font color="#ffff54">Empty throne?</font>

1636
02:10:17.700 --> 02:10:20.520
<font color="#ffff54">I've been sitting on that empty throne for 20 years!</font>

1637
02:10:21.320 --> 02:10:24.220
<font color="#ffff54">My knowledge. my years of experience.</font>

1638
02:10:24.420 --> 02:10:26.560
<font color="#ffff54">that's all nothing compared with the bristles on your chin!</font>

1639
02:10:29.840 --> 02:10:30.700
<font color="#ffff54">Do you want peace?</font>

1640
02:10:31.700 --> 02:10:32.960
<font color="#ffff54">Or do you want revenge?</font>

1641
02:10:33.080 --> 02:10:34.020
<font color="#ffff54">I want Odysseus!</font>

1642
02:10:37.340 --> 02:10:38.040
<font color="#ffff54">Sing!</font>

1643
02:10:38.780 --> 02:10:40.320
<font color="#ffff54">Muse of a face!</font>

1644
02:10:43.600 --> 02:10:44.720
<font color="#ffff54">A face!</font>

1645
02:10:49.530 --> 02:10:50.160
<font color="#ffff54">A fleet!</font>

1646
02:10:54.500 --> 02:10:55.760
<font color="#ffff54">A war!</font>

1647
02:11:00.320 --> 02:11:01.160
<font color="#ffff54">At Troy!</font>

1648
02:11:05.280 --> 02:11:07.280
<font color="#ffff54">Sing news of a man!</font>

1649
02:11:11.160 --> 02:11:12.320
<font color="#ffff54">A man!</font>

1650
02:11:16.900 --> 02:11:17.700
<font color="#ffff54">Let's go!</font>

1651
02:11:21.780 --> 02:11:22.660
<font color="#ffff54">A British!</font>

1652
02:11:27.080 --> 02:11:28.140
<font color="#ffff54">Ymaes. go ahead.</font>

1653
02:11:35.360 --> 02:11:35.960
<font color="#ffff54">jacket.</font>

1654
02:11:58.840 --> 02:12:00.780
<font color="#ffff54">You should bury him up on the cliffs.</font>

1655
02:12:02.900 --> 02:12:03.960
<font color="#ffff54">Where you met?</font>

1656
02:12:12.600 --> 02:12:14.160
<font color="#ffff54">you're Odysseus</font>

1657
02:12:17.100 --> 02:12:18.500
<font color="#ffff54">you're my father</font>

1658
02:12:21.080 --> 02:12:22.460
<font color="#ffff54">I'm a beggar</font>

1659
02:12:25.680 --> 02:12:26.900
<font color="#ffff54">and you</font>

1660
02:12:28.800 --> 02:12:30.220
<font color="#ffff54">are the worthy</font>

1661
02:12:31.700 --> 02:12:33.040
<font color="#ffff54">beautiful son</font>

1662
02:12:33.040 --> 02:12:34.840
<font color="#ffff54">of Odysseus</font>

1663
02:12:36.120 --> 02:12:37.320
<font color="#ffff54">of whom</font>

1664
02:12:37.320 --> 02:12:39.700
<font color="#ffff54">when you do finally meet</font>

1665
02:12:41.700 --> 02:12:43.300
<font color="#ffff54">he will be so proud</font>

1666
02:12:47.360 --> 02:12:48.340
<font color="#ffff54">welcome home</font>

1667
02:12:49.060 --> 02:12:49.700
<font color="#ffff54">stranger</font>

1668
02:12:53.320 --> 02:12:55.180
<font color="#ffff54">because the darkness of victory</font>

1669
02:12:56.520 --> 02:12:57.560
<font color="#ffff54">shrouds the writers</font>

1670
02:12:57.560 --> 02:12:58.140
<font color="#ffff54">and legends</font>

1671
02:13:00.280 --> 02:13:01.500
<font color="#ffff54">and make bards</font>

1672
02:13:01.500 --> 02:13:03.100
<font color="#ffff54">and blind beggars of us all</font>

1673
02:13:10.680 --> 02:13:12.580
<font color="#ffff54">accept the hospitality of Zeus</font>

1674
02:13:12.580 --> 02:13:14.700
<font color="#ffff54">get the stranger some food</font>

1675
02:13:14.700 --> 02:13:15.760
<font color="#ffff54">no sir</font>

1676
02:13:16.800 --> 02:13:18.700
<font color="#ffff54">I'll just make their hands with a bull</font>

1677
02:13:24.280 --> 02:13:26.800
<font color="#ffff54">had to invite another one of these filthy plate licors today</font>

1678
02:13:26.800 --> 02:13:28.900
<font color="#ffff54">what's one more beggar at this feast</font>

1679
02:13:47.010 --> 02:13:49.630
<font color="#ffff54">we need to kill him before he regains his position with the elders</font>

1680
02:13:49.630 --> 02:13:50.330
<font color="#ffff54">how</font>

1681
02:14:09.280 --> 02:14:10.840
<font color="#ffff54">get him to grab one of the weapons</font>

1682
02:14:15.470 --> 02:14:17.170
<font color="#ffff54">he's not the same young pup</font>

1683
02:14:17.170 --> 02:14:17.950
<font color="#ffff54">he used to be</font>

1684
02:14:17.950 --> 02:14:19.650
<font color="#ffff54">when we come back tonight</font>

1685
02:14:19.650 --> 02:14:20.850
<font color="#ffff54">let me cut his tongue</font>

1686
02:14:22.110 --> 02:14:23.290
<font color="#ffff54">fuck off old man</font>

1687
02:14:23.290 --> 02:14:24.130
<font color="#ffff54">please</font>

1688
02:14:24.750 --> 02:14:26.130
<font color="#ffff54">it's been days since I've eaten</font>

1689
02:14:26.130 --> 02:14:27.350
<font color="#ffff54">I told you to fuck off</font>

1690
02:14:27.350 --> 02:14:29.110
<font color="#ffff54">you can't be generous with food</font>

1691
02:14:29.110 --> 02:14:30.250
<font color="#ffff54">that's not even yours</font>

1692
02:14:32.390 --> 02:14:33.770
<font color="#ffff54">there's no room in your bowl</font>

1693
02:14:33.770 --> 02:14:34.910
<font color="#ffff54">yes there is</font>

1694
02:14:40.860 --> 02:14:41.800
<font color="#ffff54">so there is</font>

1695
02:14:43.640 --> 02:14:44.400
<font color="#ffff54">there you go</font>

1696
02:14:48.780 --> 02:14:50.720
<font color="#ffff54">I suppose you want something for me now</font>

1697
02:14:50.720 --> 02:14:51.260
<font color="#ffff54">no</font>

1698
02:14:52.340 --> 02:14:54.100
<font color="#ffff54">I have something for you</font>

1699
02:14:54.960 --> 02:14:56.260
<font color="#ffff54">you have something for me</font>

1700
02:14:57.460 --> 02:14:58.820
<font color="#ffff54">you have something for me</font>

